  • New Sensor, New insights. The new blood oxygen sensor is made up of four LED clusters and four photodiodes. Incorporated into the completely redesigned back crystal, this new sensor works in concert with the Blood Oxygen app to determine your blood oxygen level

Name: Crossbeats TORQ Wireless Headphones Black
Short description:
• 4 in-built microphones
  • Environmental noise cancelling
  • Type-C + Wireless charging
  • 3 days of Playtime
  • IPX6 Water Resistant
  • Feather touch sensors
  • In-ear music detection
  • Qualcomm surround audio
Description:
Crossbeats Torq is the epitome of True Wireless Bluetooth earphones, a sound powerhouse crafted for the concerts you wish to live in the inside of your head.

Latest in-ear detection sensor technology have been integrated with the Crossbeats Torq to elevate your music listening experience.

Music, movies, audio calls – the Torq with its 2000mAh powerhouse delivers all this and more for 3 long days of total playtime.

Bye bye to noisy ambient audio. The beast of a Torq comes with not one, not two but four microphones so your voice is the only thing that’s heard. Take your calls with peace now, and work from home with ease.Good music is therapy, and music with Qualcomm aptX* on the Torq is craziness. Pop in the Torq and take off to a different dimension.

Enjoy the best of Apple and Google’s voice assistants that can perform tasks on your command. Set reminders, calendar schedules, calls and a lot more with these interactive best friends on the Torq.

Your all weather-ally has just evolved. The Crossbeats Torq is designed to endure elements and survive rains, accidental water splashes and outdoor dust and particles. With a resistance grade of IPX6, you can now quit being lazy at home and explore nature with your favorite music.

Name: Xiaomi mi smart scale 2 White
Short description:
• Built with inner strength, you can trust it to offer you utmost precision
  • Graphical LED display that brightens up on its own
  • Measures the weight as well as the body fat percentage
Description:
High-precision accuracy : 

Understand your body better with Mi Body Composition scale which produces accurate stats via a series of complex algorithms and advanced Bioelectrical Impedance Analysis (BIA). Now take data-driven measures to meet your health goals.

Mi Fit app : 

To give you a realistic picture of your health and fitness, Mi Body Composition Scale syncs your data to Mi Fit app so that you can see all your data in one easy-to-read graph - making easier to track your progress and take control of your activities.

Personal planner that keeps track of your progress:

Mi Fit app keep a track of different characteristics of your body composition like body weight, fat percentage, body water percentage and more to provide you with a complete training program.

  • Health data
  • Smart sorting
  • Activity data
  • Detailed records
  • Goal setting
  • Monitor progress

Name: HUAWEI FreeBuds 3i White
Short description:
• Ultimate Active Noise Cancellation
  • 3-mic System, Let the world hear your voice
  • Petit size, Mighty sound
Description:
Fits Your Ears, Fits Your Style

With their cone-shaped main bodies ergonomically crafted for style and fit, these in-ear earphones offer an immersive acoustic experience.

Pair them with the flexible silicone tips that come in 4 different sizes for a comfortable and secure fit.

Better shape, better sound.

Ultimate Active Noise Cancellation

While the outward-facing mic is detecting ambient noise to actively counter with the anti-noise, the inward-facing mic is picking up the rest noise in your ears for further cancellation.

HUAWEI FreeBuds 3i offers a thorough noise-cancelling experience for your immersive enjoyment.

Pure Delight, Free from Noise

HUAWEI FreeBuds 3i creates an ideal listening atmosphere by lowering the noise level down by up to 32dB.

Listen to high-fidelity music, thrilling movie audio effects and clear voices from love ones, and enjoy uninterrupted moments with your favorite sounds.

3-mic System, Let the World Hear Your Voice

HUAWEI FreeBuds 3i comes with two outward-facing mics to accurately pick up your voice while avoiding other environmental noises, and a third inward-facing mic receives the voice conducted inside your ears to further enhance call quality. Everything you say is clear regardless of the noises.

Pop to Pair, Ready to Start

Pair HUAWEI FreeBuds 3i automatically with the pop-up window when the charging case is open, and you are good to go. Battery status is also visible when pairing. Instantly enjoy your favorite music.

Name: HUAWEI WATCH FIT Graphite Black
Short description:
• Personalize the theme to match your everyday look with various colourful watch faces
  • 24-Hour Heart Rate Monitoring
  • With the quick charge technology, the watch can support you a whole day with only 5-minute charge
  • Now the functions that matter on the watch face can be customised easily
  • Auto-brightness adjustment offers better viewing in sunlight
Description:
Refresh Your Everyday Style

Personalizing the theme to match your everyday look with various colorful watch faces in addition to the official ones, there are abundant stunning watch faces in the Watch Face Store for you to choose from. And also you can customize your own with any photo from your mobile device.

Customized for Your Convenience

Now the functions that matter on the watch face can be customized easily. What you care about most like weather, heart rate, steps, battery life and others are free to be selected and set on a suitable position according to your viewing habits.

Any Style You Want

The textured matte watch frame pairs perfectly with the colorful and soft straps for a premium and solid design. HUAWEI WATCH FIT brings you a sophisticated and trendy look all the time.

Lighter Design Longer Battery Life

The incredibly thin and light HUAWEI WATCH FIT packs upgraded battery performance into just 21 grams, making it a perfect all-day companion. Featuring the dual chipset architecture and power-saving algorithms, this watch can last for 10 days. And with quick charge technology, the watch can support you a whole day with only 5-minute charge.

Private Trainer on Your Watch

Start training anytime with HUAWEI WATCH FIT and be free from searching for workout demonstration videos. This watch provides 12 kinds of animated quick-workouts like Exercise at Work, Full-Body Stretch, Ab ripper and includes 44 standard movement demonstrations. Make the best of your down time like coffee breaks or lazy hours on the weekend to keep fit with this smartwatch.

Stay Motivated Every Day

HUAWEI WATCH FIT tracks your fitness progress all day and reminds you to stand up every once in a while to prevent you from excessive sitting. The watch records your daily step count, hours active, and periods of medium to high-intensity activities in three colourful circles, and provides you a sense of accomplishment when completing them.

24-Hour Heart Rate Monitoring

Thanks to HUAWEI TruSeen 4.0 heart rate monitoring technology, this smart watch can accurately monitor your heart rate in real-time during the day even when you are sleeping. And timely detect if your heart rate exceeds the normal range, and send out a reminder to provide you with all-day health protection.

Name: HUAWEI Watch Fit Sakura Pink
Short description:
Highlights

  • Personalize the theme to match your everyday look with various colourful watch faces
  • 24-Hour Heart Rate Monitoring
  • With the quick charge technology, the watch can support you a whole day with only 5-minute charge
  • Now the functions that matter on the watch face can be customised easily
  • Auto-brightness adjustment offers better viewing in sunlight
Description:
Refresh Your Everyday Style

Personalizing the theme to match your everyday look with various colorful watch faces in addition to the official ones, there are abundant stunning watch faces in the Watch Face Store for you to choose from. And also you can customize your own with any photo from your mobile device.

Customized for Your Convenience

Now the functions that matter on the watch face can be customized easily. What you care about most like weather, heart rate, steps, battery life and others are free to be selected and set on a suitable position according to your viewing habits.

Any Style You Want

The textured matte watch frame pairs perfectly with the colorful and soft straps for a premium and solid design. HUAWEI WATCH FIT brings you a sophisticated and trendy look all the time.

Lighter Design Longer Battery Life

The incredibly thin and light HUAWEI WATCH FIT packs upgraded battery performance into just 21 grams, making it a perfect all-day companion. Featuring the dual chipset architecture and power-saving algorithms, this watch can last for 10 days. And with quick charge technology, the watch can support you a whole day with only 5-minute charge.

Private Trainer on Your Watch

Start training anytime with HUAWEI WATCH FIT and be free from searching for workout demonstration videos. This watch provides 12 kinds of animated quick-workouts like Exercise at Work, Full-Body Stretch, Ab ripper and includes 44 standard movement demonstrations. Make the best of your down time like coffee breaks or lazy hours on the weekend to keep fit with this smartwatch.

Stay Motivated Every Day

HUAWEI WATCH FIT tracks your fitness progress all day and reminds you to stand up every once in a while to prevent you from excessive sitting. The watch records your daily step count, hours active, and periods of medium to high-intensity activities in three colourful circles, and provides you a sense of accomplishment when completing them.

24-Hour Heart Rate Monitoring

Thanks to HUAWEI TruSeen 4.0 heart rate monitoring technology, this smart watch can accurately monitor your heart rate in real-time during the day even when you are sleeping. And timely detect if your heart rate exceeds the normal range, and send out a reminder to provide you with all-day health protection.
Categories: Smart Watches, Smart Watches > Smart Watches

Name: Apple AirPods Pro Wireless Earphones White
Short description:
• Active Noise Cancellation
  • Transparency mode
  • Amazing sound quality with Adaptive EQ
  • Sweat and water resistant (IPX4)²
  • Automatically on, automatically connected
  • Easy setup for all your Apple devices³
  • Quick charging in the case
  • Case can be charged either wirelessly using a Qi-certified charger or with the Lightning connector
Description:
Magic like you’ve never heard

AirPods Pro have been designed to deliver Active Noise Cancellation for immersive sound, Transparency mode so you can hear your surroundings, and a customizable fit for all-day comfort. Just like AirPods, AirPods Pro connect magically to your iPhone or Apple Watch. And they’re ready to use right out of the case.

Active Noise Cancellation

Incredibly light noise-cancelling headphones, AirPods Pro block out your environment so you can focus on what you’re listening to. AirPods Pro use two microphones, an outward-facing microphone and an inward-facing microphone, to create superior noise cancellation. By continuously adapting to the geometry of your ear and the fit of the ear tips, Active Noise Cancellation silences the world to keep you fully tuned in to your music, podcasts, and calls.

Transparency mode

Switch to Transparency mode and AirPods Pro let the outside sound in, allowing you to hear and connect to your surroundings. Outward- and inward-facing microphones enable AirPods Pro to undo the sound-isolating effect of the silicone tips so things sound and feel natural, like when you’re talking to people around you.

All-new design

AirPods Pro offer a more customizable fit with three sizes of flexible silicone tips to choose from. With an internal taper, they conform to the shape of your ear, securing your AirPods Pro in place and creating an exceptional seal for superior noise cancellation.

Amazing audio quality

A custom-built high-excursion, low-distortion driver delivers powerful bass. A superefficient high dynamic range amplifier produces pure, incredibly clear sound while also extending battery life. And Adaptive EQ automatically tunes music to suit the shape of your ear for a rich, consistent listening experience.

Even more magical

The Apple-designed H1 chip delivers incredibly low audio latency. A force sensor on the stem makes it easy to control music and calls and switch between Active Noise Cancellation and Transparency mode. Announce Messages with Siri gives you the option to have Siri read your messages through your AirPods. And with Audio Sharing, you and a friend can share the same audio stream on two sets of AirPods — so you can play a game, watch a movie, or listen to a song together.¹

Name: JBL Portable Bluetooth Party Speaker PARTYBOX Black
Short description:
• Powerful JBL Pro Sound
  • Light up the night
  • Keep the party going
Description:
Bluetooth® party speaker with synchronised light show

Loudspeaker drivers: 2x 17.6cm (6.5″) woofers, 2x 6.5cm (2.5″) tweeters

Total output power: 240W RMS

Frequency range: 45Hz to 20kHz

Digital input: Bluetooth®, USB-9dBFS

USB format: FAT16, FAT32

USB file format: MP3, WMA, WAV

USB output: 5V/2.1A

Bluetooth® range: approx. 10m

Bluetooth® version: 5.1

Protected against splash water in accordance with the IPX4 standard*

Power supply via battery and mains adapter (100 to 240V, 50/60Hz)

Standby power consumption: <2W with BT connection; <0.5W without BT connection

Lithium-ion battery (72Wh, runtime up to 18 hrs., charging time up to 1.5 hrs.)

 

The JBL Bluetooth® Partybox 310 delivers powerful sound and spectacular, synced light effects that automatically groove to the beat for great party vibes- both indoors and outdoors, in a park or on the beach. The box is splash-proof*, can withstand the occasional light shower and will keep the party going for up to 18 hours without a power connection, thanks to its powerful battery. Or you can use the mains adapter and ensure good vibes around the clock. An absolute power pack with a total output of 240 watts.

Name: JBL Portable Bluetooth Speaker FLIP5 Black
Short description:
• built-in Bluetooth 4.2 for streaming music from your smartphone or tablet
  • IPX7-rated waterproof — can be submerged down to 1 meter for up to 30 minutes
  • splash-proof fabric cover and durable rubber housing
  • 1-3/4" x 3-1/8" transducer with dual passive bass radiators
  • frequency response: 65-20,000 Hz
Description:
Groove on the go with the powerful JBL Flip 5 in a vivid red shade. This lightweight Bluetooth speaker goes anywhere you want. With its waterproof design, dance in the rain like no one’s watching! Enjoy more than 12 hours of play time of your favorite music and party hard with linking multiple JBL partyboost-compatible speakers to create a bigger party. Choose the color of your choice with 11 vivid options while keeping it vertical or horizontal, just as you please.

Sounds better than ever Feel your music. Flip 5’s all new racetrack-shaped driver delivers high output. Enjoy booming bass in a compact package Bring the party anywhere Don’t sweat the small stuff like charging your battery. Flip 5 gives you more than 12 hours of playtime. Keep the music going longer and louder with JBL’s signature sound Make a splash with IPX7 waterproof design Bring your speakers anywhere. Pool party? Perfect. Sudden cloudburst? Covered. Bash on the beach? Flip 5 is IPX7 waterproof up to three-feet deep for fearless outdoor entertainment Crank up the fun with PartyBoost PartyBoost allows you to pair two JBL PartyBoost-compatible speakers together for stereo sound or link multiple JBL PartyBoost-compatible speakers to pump up your party A rainbow of colours With 11 distinct colour options, the Flip 5 is anything but boring. Broaden your spectrum with JBL’s signature sound Tough as it sounds Slip this little gem onto your wrist and get grooving. Its durable fabric material and rugged rubber housing keep the Flip 5 safe while you let loose in the great outdoors

Name: JBL Full-Featured Waterproof Ultra-Portable Speaker CLIP3 Black
Short description:
• Bluetooth Wireless Streaming
  • Waterproof in up to 3.3' of Water
  • IPX7 Rated
  • Can Double as a Speakerphone
  • Output power: 3.3W
  • Music playing time: 10hrs
  • Bluetooth version: 4.1
  • Battery capacity: 1000mAh
  • Charging Time: 3hrs
Description: Like no other, the JBL Clip 3 is a unique ultra-portable, ultra-rugged and waterproof Bluetooth® speaker that is small in size but with surprisingly big sound. The upgraded durable and fully integrated carabiner clips to your clothes, belt loop or backpack, making the Clip 3 your outdoor companion on every adventure. The Clip 3 is IPX7 waterproof and offers 10 hours of playtime, powered by a 1000mAh rechargeable Li-ion battery, allowing you to bring your music with you. A built-in noise and echo-cancelling speakerphone gives you crystal clear calls with the press of a button.

• Designed to deliver big audio and punchy bass from a compact design.
  • A portable design, colorful fabric, and expressive details help the Go 3 look as good as it sounds
  • The Go 3 is waterproof and dustproof, so you can bring it to the pool, park, and just about everywhere
  • Stream music from your phone, tablet, or any compatible Bluetooth-enabled device wirelessly
  • The Go 3 provides up to five hours of play time on a single charge
  • Integrated loop lets you carry the Go 3 nearly anywhere
  • 2.5-hour charge time
Description: JBL Go 3 features bold styling and rich JBL Pro Sound. With its new eye-catching edgy design, colorful fabrics and expressive details this a must-have accessory for your next outing. Your tunes will lift you up with JBL Pro Sound, it’s IP67 waterproof and dustproof so you can keep listening rain or shine, and with its integrated loop, you can carry it anywhere. Go 3 comes in completely new shades and color combinations inspired by current street fashion. JBL Go 3 looks as vivid as it sounds. To the park. Name: JBL Kids Wireless On-Ear Headphone JR310BT Blue
Short description:
• JBL Safe Sound
  • Equipped with Bluetooth technology
  • Built-in microphone
  • 30-hour battery life
  • Simple controls
  • Comfortable fit
  • Fully portable
  • Customize them - JBL sticker set
Description:
Legendary sound for small ears.
Safe, lightweight and sized for kids, the JBL Jr310BT wireless headphones provide up to 30 hours of JBL legendary sound and entertainment for the youngest music fans. The headphones are designed to never exceed 85 dB for hearing protection, with controls that can be easily operated by children themselves. Kids listen in comfort thanks to the upholstered soft headband and soft-fitting earbuds. And every headphone is different, because the JBL Jr310BT headphones can be customized with affordable, reusable stickers for even more fun!

JBL Safe Sound
The legendary JBL sound is designed to never exceed 85 dB, making the headphones safe even for the youngest music fans.

Equipped with Bluetooth technology
Wireless connection within a distance of 15 meters means that you do not have to worry about any cables.

Built-
in microphone The built- in microphone will help your children stay in touch with the world. During breaks, they can easily chat with friends and family or teachers when they are busy learning.

30-hour battery life
30-hour battery life and fast charging with user-friendly USB type C. And for super fast charging, you get 2 hours of battery life after just 5 minutes of charging.

Simple controls
Child-friendly control buttons ensure easy and safe operation by children.

Comfortable fit
Soft padded voice belt and earbuds for easy fitting.

Fully portable
The combination of compact and foldable design makes music highly portable.

Personalize them - JBL Sticker set
Children can customize the headphones with stickers in the package. Inverter size: 32 mm dynamic inverter

 

Power supply: 5.0 V 1.0 A
Weight: 115 g
Battery type: Lithium-ion Polymer battery (400 mA / 3.7 V)
Charging time: <2 hours when the battery is discharged
Music playback with BT on: 30 hours
Frequency response: 20 Hz - 20 kHz
Impedance: 32 ohms
Sensitivity: 90 dB SPL @ 1 kHz 1 mW
Maximum SPL: 80 dB
Microphone sensitivity: -40 ± 3 dBV @ 1 kHz / Pa
Bluetooth version: 5.0
Bluetooth profile version: A2DP 1.3, AVRCP 1.5, HFP V1.6
Bluetooth transmitter frequency range: 2.4GHz - 2.4835 GHz
Bluetooth transmitter power: <4 dbm
Bluetooth transmitter modulation: GFSK, π / 4 DQPSK, 8DPSK
Maximum operating temperature: 45 ° C

Name: JBL On-Ear Earphone T500BT Black
Short description:
• Wireless Bluetooth streaming
  • JBL Pure Bass sound
  • Hands free calls
  • Lightweight, comfortable and foldable design
  • Multipoint connections
  • Ask Siri or Google Now
  • 16 hours play time
Description:
Full bass, all day.
The JBL TUNE500BT headphones allow you to stream powerful audio without any cable connections, for up to 16 hours of pure pleasure. Easy to use and equipped with 32 mm JBL drivers and JBL Pure Bass sound, these headphones provide quick access to unique sound at any time. And if you get a phone call while watching a video on another device, the JBL TUNE500BT will seamlessly switch your mobile phone to you. Equipped with Bluetooth technology, the JBL TUNE500BT headphones also allow you to connect to Siri or Google Now without using your mobile phone. Available in 4 bright colors with the possibility of folding for their easy portability. The JBL TUNE500BT headphones are a solution that allows you to bring music to every aspect of your busy life.

Bluetooth wireless streaming
Stream high-quality audio wirelessly from your smartphone or tablet, without the need for messy cables.

JBL Pure Bass Sound The
headphones have the renowned JBL Pure Bass sound, which can be found in the most famous places around the world.

Hands free calls
Easily control your sound and manage your phone calls from your headphones with the handy 1-button remote control with microphone.

16 hour battery life 2 hours of charging and fast charging (5 minutes = 1 hour of listening)
For long-lasting entertainment, listen wirelessly for 16 hours and charge the battery in as little as 2 hours. Fast 5-minute charging brings you another hour of listening to music.

Lightweight, comfortable and foldable design
Thanks to the light material and soft earbuds with a padded headband, these headphones are comfortable to wear for a long time. Thanks to the foldable design, these headphones are easy to wear wherever and whenever you want to listen to music.

Multipoint Connections
Allows you to easily switch from one Bluetooth® device to another. You can easily switch from the video on your tablet to a phone call on your mobile phone, so you never miss a phone call.

Ask Siri or Google Now
Siri or Google Now available with one button: activate the voice assistant by pressing the multifunction button.

 

Converter size: 32 mm dynamic converter
Frequency response: 20 Hz - 20 kHz
Bluetooth transmitter power: <4 dBm
Bluetooth transmitter modulator: GSFK, π / 4 DQPSK, 8DPSK
Bluetooth frequency: 2.402 - 2.480 GHz
Bluetooth profile: BT 4.1, A2DP v1. 2, AVRCP v1.5, HFP v1.6, HSP v1.2
Battery type: Polymeric li-ion battery (3.7 V, 300 mAH)
Charging time: 2 hours
Music playback time with BT function on: 16 hours
Weight: 148 g

• JBL Characteristic Sound
  • Get help from your voice assistant
  • Press play. Clear distractions
  • Hands-free phone calls
  • Multipoint connections

Description:
Enjoy your music without cables and disturbing ambient sounds
Great sound is important in your world, so put the JBL LIVE 650BTNC wireless headphones on your ears with noise reduction and enhance your day. Equipped with powerful 40 mm drivers, the JBL LIVE650BTNC headphones deliver the distinctive JBL sound, which features enhanced bass, so every track in every playlist sounds. And if music is the only thing that matters, active noise cancellation technology lets you block out surrounding sounds so nothing will disturb your rhythm. Need some help overcoming this day? Simply access Google Assistant or Amazon Alexa with a single tap on the handset to play your favorite playlists, write to your friend or check the weather and much more without looking at your phone. But this is not all. With a stylish, With a light and comfortable design, you will be able to listen to your favorite music for up to 30 hours (20 hours with BT + ANC). The headphones are fully charged in just two hours, support multi-point connections and have a practical detachable cable with remote control and microphone that allows you to continue listening even if the battery runs out. Listen to your favorite music and don't be disturbed by the surrounding noise with the JBL LIVE650BTNC headphones.

The distinctive sound of the JBL
40 mm converter and the distinctive sound that you can find in the most famous places around the world.

Get help from the voice assistant
Play your favorite playlist, write to your friend, check the weather and much more by simply tapping the handset to activate the Google or Amazon Alex voice assistant service. Use the brand new JBL App to easily set your preferred voice assistants.

Press play. Cancel distraction
With the active noise canceling function, don't be disturbed by the surrounding noise and keep the noise as far away as possible and focus only on listening to your favorite music.

Hands free phone calls
Stay in touch with your world by managing phone calls with the buttons on the handset. If the battery is exhausted, just connect the audio cable and continue listening and talking.

Multipoint Connections
Allows you to easily switch from one Bluetooth® device to another. You can easily switch from video or your tablet to a phone call on your mobile phone, so you never miss a phone call.

Comfortable fabric headband
The JBL LIVE650BTNC headphones have a shaped fabric headband to hold comfortably on your head and soft earbuds for maximum comfort when listening to music.

My JBL Headphones application
Customize your listening experience by customizing the sound of the JBL LIVE650BTNC to your liking with the free My JBL Headphones app.

30 hours battery life with ANC off and fast charging
Enjoy your favorite music for 30 hours with Active Noise Canceled, or 20 hours with Bluetooth on and Active Noise Off. Fast 15-minute charging brings you another two hours of listening to music.

Keep the headphones safe
when not in use The soft case serves as protection and also as a storage location for the headphones when not in use.

Name: JBL Wireless In-Ear Headphone T115BT Black
Short description:
• JBL Pure Bass Sound
  • 8 hours battery life with quick charge function
  • Multi-point connection allows easy switching between Bluetooth devices
  • Magnetic cable guide
  • 3-button remote control with microphone
Description:
Make it easy to listen to all your music.
Equipped with JBL Pure Bass sound, the JBL TUNE 115BT headphones provide a take-and-go wireless solution for your everyday entertainment. And they have more than just great sound: The JBL TUNE 115BT headphones allow you to make or receive hands-free phone calls and provide 8 hours of battery life. Thanks to the multipoint connection option, you will never miss a phone call, as the JBL TUNE 115BT headphones seamlessly switch between the video on your tablet and the call on the phone. Imagine headphones that will be charged quickly in 2 hours, come in a variety of bold colors, are equipped with a flat cable that does not get tangled and are light enough for comfortable wearing for hours. And when we add magnets to ensure that the headphones don't hang when not in use,

JBL Pure Bass Sound
For more than 70 years, JBL has been designing the precise, impressive sound you'll find at major events around the world. These headphones reproduce the same JBL sound, delivering bass that has both depth and power.

8-hour battery life with fast charging
Built-in battery charged via micro USB, ensures 8 hours of playback, with fast charging in as little as 2 hours or 15 minutes for an extra 1 hour.

Multipoint
Allows you to effortlessly switch from one Bluetooth® device to another. You can easily switch from video on your tablet to a call on your mobile phone so you never miss a call again.

Magnetic cable routing
This ensures that the headphones remain comfortably locked and hung around your neck without tangling when not in use.

3-button remote control with microphone
Enjoy cordless phone calls and manage your music hands-free.

 

Converter size: 8.6 mm dynamic converter
Dynamic frequency response range: 20 Hz - 20 kHz
Sensitivity: 102 dB SPL / 1 kHz 1 MW
Microphone sensitivity: –25 dBV / PA 1 kHz
Impedance: 16 Ω
Bluetooth transmission power: <4 dBm
Bluetooth transmission modulation: GFSK, DQPSK, 8-DPSK
Bluetooth frequency: 2.402 GHz - 2.48 GHz
Bluetooth profiles: HFP v1.5, HSP v1.2, A2DP v1.2, AVRCP v1.5
Bluetooth version: V4.2
Battery type: Polymer Li-ion battery (3.7 V / 160 mAh)
Power supply: 5 V – 1 A
Charging time: <2 hrs.
Music playback time with BT on: 8 hours
Weight: 19.02 g

Name: JBL In-Ear Headphone Wired T110 Black
Short description:
• JBL Pure Bass sound
  • 1-button remote with microphone
  • Tangle-free flat cable
Description: Introducing JBL TUNE110 in-ear headphones. They’re lightweight, comfortable and compact. Under the durable earpiece housing, a pair of 9mm drivers punch out some serious bass, reproducing the JBL Pure Bass sound you’ve experienced in concert halls, arenas and recording studios around the world. In addition, the single-button remote on a tangle-free flat cable lets you control music playback, as well as answer calls on the fly with a built-in microphone. Making the JBL TUNE110 your everyday companion for work, at home and on the road.

Name: JBL True Wireless In-Ear Nc Headphone Black
Short description:
• Legendary JBL Pro Sound
  • Adaptive Noise Cancelling with Smart Ambient
  • Zero Hassle Connectivity
  • Even More Voice Clarity in Perfect Stereo Sound
  • All-Day Wireless Power
  • Tap To Talk
  • Comfort You Can Feel, Fit You Can Check
Description:
Legendary JBL Pro Sound
Your workday playlist sounds even more inspiring with full, immersive JBL Pro Sound. Use the JBL My Headphones app to customize the sound to your liking or choose presets from STAGE+ created by the world’s top DJs
Adaptive Noise Cancelling with Smart Ambient
In a crowded coffee shop trying to drown out the loud conversation at the next table? Activate the noise cancelling technology and stay focused. Walking in a busy street? Let in the surrounding sounds and keep walking safely. Need to have a quick chat with your coworkers? TalkThru makes it easy to do it keeping your headphones on
Zero Hassle Connectivity
Your JBL CLUB PRO+ TWS pair seamlessly to your device as soon as you flip open the case, thanks to Dual Connect + Sync technology. And no need to remember which one to grab first, because you can do all the things with either earbud, whether you’re using both or just one
Even More Voice Clarity in Perfect Stereo Sound
Have no fear about taking a call outside on a breezy day. 3-mic beamforming technology delivers crystal clear calls with all the sound you want, while eliminating the background noise you don’t
All-Day Wireless Power
Make it all the way through your workday with an 8-hour charge and 3 times more from the case (24 hours). If you need a little extra juice, just 10 minutes in the charging case will get you another hour’s use. The stylish, ergonomic charging case supports both totally wireless Qi charging and Type-C connectors
Tap To Talk
Just tap the iconic JBL logo either to talk to Google or to activate Amazon Alexa. Three sensitive mics mean your digital assistant won’t have any trouble hearing or understanding you
Comfort You Can Feel, Fit You Can Check
The unibody design inspired by professional in-ear monitors offers all-day comfort. The first time you use them, the downloaded JBL app walks you through an easy Seal Check to make sure you’re getting the best fit from the three ear tip sizes included
My JBL Headphones
Get even more control and personalization of your listening experience with this free App

 

Technical

  • Freedom From Wires
  • Listen For Longer

Description:
Feel The Bass

JBL has been powering festivals and concerts around the world for decades. Now let JBL bring your own world to life with incredible Pure Bass sound
Freedom From Wires
Tangled in your bag, caught in your jacket or stuck in your hair, wires can get in your way. Experience total freedom with no cords with the True Wireless JBL TUNE 225TWS earbuds
Listen For Longer
With up to 25 hours of battery life, you can listen all day and all night. Keep your own private concert going for as long as you can keep up
Either Ear, Or Both
Left ear, right ear, both ears? The power of Dual Connect gives you the choice to seamlessly enjoy music or make calls with either one or both buds. And the battery life keeps up with you, as you can keep one earbud charging, while using the other one
Find Your Style
What works for you? With 6 different colors, you’ll be able to find the perfect pair of earbuds to match exactly who you are
Sleek, convenient charging case
No detail left to chance. The charging case for the JBL TUNE 225TWS is as thoughtfully designed as the earbuds it holds, with a shape inspired by a river stone, a soft body, and a curved lid that pops up to give you fast access to your buds

Name: JBL Wireless In-Ear Headphones 220TWS Black
Short description:
• JBL Pure Bass
  • 19 Hours Of Combined Playback
  • Convenient Buttons On The Right And Left Earbuds For Switching Tracks, Playing, Pausing, Voice Command, And Taking calls
  • Hands-Free Stereo Calls
  • Sleek, Convenient Charging Case
Description:
JBL Pure Bass
JBL TUNE 220TWS earbuds don’t go for average, but play standout audio. With a 12mm driver featuring JBL Pure Bass Sound, they do not skimp on sound.
19 hours of combined playback: the sound never quits
Find your groove and stay in it. These earbuds give you up to 3 hours of nonstop sound plus another 16 hours from the pocket-sized charging case.
Stay connected, not wired
No annoying wires, no tangles — just your music when and where you want it, compatible with both iPhone and Android devices. From wire-free music, seamlessly connected thanks to Bluetooth 5.0, to hands-free calls, they keep up while you keep moving.
Easy, on-the-go controls
Go from playlist to call to Voice Assistant without missing a beat. Convenient buttons on the right and left earbuds for switching tracks, playing, pausing, voice command, and taking calls put you in control every step of the way.
Hands-free, fuss-free stereo calls
Grabbing a call mid-song doesn’t have to interrupt your flow. Switch back and forth with on-ear controls and go hands-free for stereo-mode calls that are completely distortion-free.
Turn your style up a notch
They may be small in size but they have a big wow factor, with a sleek metallic finish and soft-touch paint. Go classic white or choose from an array of both trendy and classic colors to match your style.
Designed for all-day wear
You’ll want to keep them in your ears non-stop — and thanks to the comfortable ergonomic design, you’ll be able to. The JBL TUNE 220TWS earbuds were designed with all-day wear in mind.
Sleek, convenient charging case
No detail left to chance. The charging case for the JBL TUNE 220TWS is as thoughtfully designed as the earbuds it holds, with a shape inspired by a river stone, a soft body, and a curved lid that pops up to give you fast access to your buds.
Specifications:

Driver Size: 12mm dynamic driver
Frequency Response: 20Hz – 20kHz
Sensitivity: 105dB SPL
Maximum SPL: 98dB SPL
Microphone sensitivity: -30dBV@1kHz/Pa
Impedance: 32 ohm
Bluetooth transmitted power: 11dBm
Bluetooth transmitted modulation: GFSK, π/4 DQPSK, 8DPSK
Bluetooth frequency: 2.402GHz – 2.48GHz
Bluetooth profile version: A2DP 1.3, AVRCP 1.5, HFP 1.6
Bluetooth version: 5.0
Headset Battery type: Lithium-ion Battery (22mA/3.85V)
Charging case Battery type: Lithium-ion (410mA/3.85V)
Charging time: <2 hours from empty
Music playtime with BT on: 3 hrs
Total music playtime with charging case: 19 hrs

Name: JBL Wireless In-Ear Headphone T125TWS Black

  • Truly Wireless

Description:
Feel The Bass
JBL has powered festivals and concerts around the world for decades. Now let JBL bring your own world to life with incredible Pure Bass sound
Freedom From Wires
Tangled in your bag, caught in your jacket or stuck in your hair, wires can get in your way. Experience total freedom with no cords with the True Wireless JBL TUNE 125TWS earbuds
Listen For Longer

Name: JBL Truly Wireless In-Ear Headphone FREE X Black
Short description:
• Truly wireless
  • JBL Signature Sound
  • 24 hours of combined playback
Description:
Truly wireless
Discover the freedom of a wireless lifestyle listening to music, managing your calls or working-out. JBL Free truly wireless in-ear headphones deliver JBL Signature Sound in an intuitive, yet intelligent package. Completely free from wires and easy to use, the JBL Free is your flexible companion for calls, music and an active lifestyle.

JBL Signature Sound
Immersive JBL Signature Sound delivered in an intuitive, intelligent package. The splashproof worry free IPX5 certified design keeps the music playing through sunshine and rain. Step up your listening experience in three easy ways:
(1) use one earbud for calls
(2) use two earbuds for immersive music
(3) add the gel sleeves for secure fit during workouts.

24 hours of combined playback
Enjoy an entire day of wireless audio, with 4 hours of continuous playback and 20 hours of backup power from the charging case. You get 24 hours of combined playback: 4hrs of continuous listening on the headphones plus 20 hours of backup from the smart charging case. Comfort Stay Secure Fit ergonomics with 3 ear-tip and 2 gel sleeve sizes provide a tailored fit for all day wear and active use.

Name: JBL Wireless In-Ear Headphones LIVE 300TWS Black
Short description:
• JBL Signature Sound
  • Truly Wireless
  • Ambient Aware
  • 6 Hours Battery Life + 14 Hour Charge in Case
  • Ergonomic Fit
  • Connectivity Technology: Bluetooth
  • Wireless Communication Technology: Bluetooth
Description:
JBL Signature Sound
Small in size, but packing serious power, JBL LIVE 300TWS headphones deliver the audio you expect from JBL.
Ambient Aware and TalkThru technology
Control the world around you. Instantly move from absolute music immersion to focus on your surroundings with Ambient Aware. Chat with your friends without removing your headphones with TalkThru. Just swipe on the earbuds to activate them.
Be free with True Wireless
JBL LIVE 300TWS headphones are totally wireless, with nothing to hold you back or tie you down.
Hands-free stereo calls
Wherever you are in the world, and whatever you are doing, take your music along for the ride and stay connected with perfect, stereo clear calls with no background noise. Discover total listening freedom with hands-free functionality and no distractions with all-access touch control.
Instant access to Voice Assistants
Voice Assistant gives you the convenience of the Google Assistant and Amazon Alexa in your ears, making it even easier to get what you want. Choose yours with the My JBL headphones app and you are all set. Just swipe on the earbuds to activate them.
My JBL Headphones App
Personalize your listening experience by tweaking the JBL LIVE 300TWS sound preferences via the free My JBL Headphones App.
20 hours of combined playback: Never stop playing
Never be without your music. JBL LIVE 300TWS headphones give you 6 hours of playback on a single charge. Pop them into the charging case for an additional 14 hours of listening. Get a one-hour boost in just 10 minutes.
Good looking (also when off)
Pick the pair that suits you. JBL LIVE 300TWS headphones are super stylish, and come in a range of colors.
Comfort-secure fit
Listen all day in complete comfort. JBL LIVE 300TWS headphones have four available sizes of wing fin stabilizers.
Sweat and water resistant
Never let bad weather or a tough workout hold you back. JBL LIVE 300TWS headphones are sweat-proof and water-resistant with an IPX5 certification.

Name: JBL Waterproof True Wireless In-Ear Headphones REFLMININC Black
Short description:
• Noise-canceling headphones
  • Bluetooth 5.1
  • 21 hours playback time (earphone: 7 hours; charging box: 14 hours)
  • Active noise-cancelling with smart ambient
  • Ear clip for secure fit
  • JBL Signature Sound
Description:
Designed for movement, defined by you.
Whether yoga, running or ballet rod: JBL Reflect Mini NC in-ear sports headphones are the perfect accessory for your athlete lifestyle. Active noise-cancelling allows you to focus on your fitness goal without distractions, while smart ambient technology keeps you in the middle of your surroundings and talking to friends. Each in-ear earphone connects immediately and independantly, so that you can answer calls with each of them and assign individual functions to them. With 21 hours playback time, various reflective color options and IPX7 water resistance, they are the ultimate in-ear wireless headphones.

21 hours playback time (earphone: 7 hours; charging box: 14 hours)
Long battery life means you can get to the limit much longer without worrying about charging.

Active noise-cancelling with smart ambient
Hide what wasn't you want to hear or hear what was you want to hear. Smart Ambient technology keeps you safe on the road or chatting with a friend during training.

Ear clip for secure fit
Choose from three stabilizing earloops to find a snug, stable, and comfortable fit.

JBL Signature Sound
An excellent sound for indoor and outdoor training gives you the right motivation in every situation.

Multi-AI integrated
Keep it simple. Hey Google or Amazon Alexa was making all you wanted right away.

Waterproof with reflective accents
Don't worry! With IPX7 water resistance/sweat resistance, you can get as wet as you want without worrying about it. With a reflective JBL logo for better visibility and a choice of cool colors, you can be stylish and secure at the same time.

Dual Connect + Sync technology
It doesn't matter which headphones you take out of the box first. You can answer calls, adjust the volume, or use the voice assistant on each ear to help you stay flexible and stay on top of your swing.

Hands-free stereo calls with auto-pause
Your in-ear headphones do that. The microphones on the left and right take up your voice in stereo when making calls. When you take them out, they stop the music. You don't even have to think about it.

My JBL headphones
Get even more control and personalization for your listening experience with this free app.

Name: LG Xboom Speaker OM4560 Black
Short description:
• 220W
  • Karaoke Star
  • Multi Color Lighting
  • Shared Jukebox
  • Bluetooth® Connectivity
  • DVD Player
  • TV Sound Sync
Description:
Compact Size, Big Sound
LG XBOOM OL45 gets the party going with powerful 220-watt sound and thumping bass.

Multi Color Lighting
Colored lights flash in sync with the music to add excitement and atmosphere to parties.

Karaoke Star
Singing is easy and enjoyable with a voice canceller to reduce in-track vocals and a key changer that tunes the music to your voice. You can also choose 18 different vocal effects to sing with.

Double Your Sound with Wireless Party Link
Link two LG XBOOM OL45 systems together wirelessly to increase the output to 440 watts. An extra speaker means more powerful sound and more fun.

Versatile Connectivity
Choose from a variety of input options including Bluetooth®, USB, CD and FM Radio.

Be More Immersed with TV Sound Sync
Connect the OL45 to your LG TV via Bluetooth® to experience more impressive, room-filling sound.

Name: LG Boom Blast Multimedia Speakers LK72B Black
Short description:
• Bass Blast+
  • Wireless Audio Streaming
  • Bass Volume Control
  • FM Radio
  • Easy Connectivity
Description:
Wireless Audio Streaming via Bluetooth: Easily connect your mobile devices via Bluetooth and enjoy your favorite music using the LG XBOOM LK72B.

Specially Designed Remote Control: You can separately control the bass level of the music for a personalized listening experience.

FM Radio Playback: Tune in to any FM radio station to listen your favorite radio shows and music.

Port.
In/Aux In: Easily connect your PC, laptop, tablet, game console or mobile phone to LG XBOOM LK72B via Port.
In and Aux In.

USB & SD Card Playback: Just plug a USB memory drive or SD Card loaded with music into your LG XBOOM LK72B speaker system to enjoy your favorite music.

Wall Mountable: LG XBOOM LK72B satellite speakers can easily be mounted on the wall, saving space and making them an integral part of your TV.

Name: LG Wireless Bluetooth Party Speaker PK7-BK Black
Short description:
• Easy Bluetooth pairing and high definition streaming
  • Up to 22 hours playback
  • Enhanced bass with LED beat lighting
  • Water and weather resistant (iPX5 rated)
  • Dual play connection - enjoy stereo sound by wirelessly pairing two PK7 speakers (PK7 speakers sold separately)
Description:
Bluetooth Portable
For even greater versatility, the XBOOM Go PK7 portable speaker is Bluetooth-enabled with its own built-in rechargeable battery, allowing it to be enjoyed just about anywhere

Up to 22-Hour Playback
The party may end, but the XBOOM Go PK7 keeps going and going. The built-in battery of this fully portable Bluetooth speaker allows it to play up to twenty two hours between charges. (Battery life will vary depending on usage conditions.)

Weather-Resistant / Splash-Resistant
No one likes to let a little weather stop the party, so the PK7 speaker system is weather and splash resistant, and keeps rocking when other outdoor speakers have packed up and headed home.

Dual Play Mode
Enjoy stereo sound by wirelessly pairing two PK speakers* To activate the Dual Play mode connect one speaker to a device via Bluetooth. Next, press and hold the “+” on the back of both speakers and listen for the tone to indicate the speakers have been paired and Dual Play mode is on. Then, enjoy your music in full, rich stereo sound. (*PK5 and PK7 speakers sold separately.)

Bluetooth Speakerphone
Talk on the phone through the speaker. The built-in microphone automatically filters audio so calls are loud and clear. Just answer the phone with the touch of a button and talk freely. Music is automatically muted for a truly hands-free conversation.

Meridian Audio with Enhanced Bass
Enjoy sound quality previously unavailable in a Bluetooth speaker. Technology from the renowned experts at Meridian Audio combines advanced signal processing and hardware design to expand image height and widen the sound field, with custom Clear Vocal and Enhanced Bass presets for uncompromising performance.

Dual Tweeters
Enjoy music more than ever with clearer instruments and voices. The powerful PK7 XBOOM Go Bluetooth speaker distributes its high frequencies across two separate tweeters for more precise sonic detail.

Name: LG Portable Bluetooth Speaker PK5-BK Black
Short description:
• Portability meets Party-Ability
  • LG Partners with MERIDIAN Audio
  • Enhanced Bass & Clear Vocal
  • Multi Colour Lighting
  • X-Grip Design
  • High Fidelity Bluetooth
Description:
Exceptional Sound Everywhere
LG XBOOM Go PK5 outputs powerful bass, and Meridian's premium tuning works to give you quality sound wherever you go. Be amazed every time you hit play

with MERIDIAN
LG partnered with Meridian - the pioneers of high resolution audio – to deliver exceptional sound. Tune in for a richer, more intense audio experience.

Enhanced Bass and Clear Vocal
Get amazing full range coverage with Meridian technology. Enhanced Bass adds greater depth to your sound for a more immersive audio experience. Clear Vocal fine-tunes the high tones for crisper sound at an enjoyable volume.

Powerful Dual Action Bass
Dual Action Bass amplifies low frequencies for bolder and more powerful beats that will keep the party going.

Lossless Streaming with aptX HD
Conveniently pair and listen to music at better than CD quality with LG XBOOM Go. aptX HD delivers 24-bit music over a Bluetooth® connection.

Long Lasting Battery
LG XBOOM Go PK5 has a built-in battery that can last up to 18 hours. Party all night without worrying about recharge.

Weather-Resistant
No need to worry about the rain or splashes from the pool with an IPX5 waterproof protecting rating.

Grab & Go with X-Grip
X-Grip makes it easy to take your music with you wherever you go. Handgrips on the top and bottom are designed to give you both stability on ground and better portability on foot.

Share the Playlist with Multi Bluetooth
The PK5 lets you to pair two devices at the same time via Bluetooth®. Seamlessly control a playlist with any of connected devices with no interruption to music.

Voice Command for Remote Control
Activate the Google Assistant on your smartphone with the Voice Command button. Pause or play the next track simply with your voice all without touching your smartphone.

Multi Colour Lighting
Light up the party with colourful LED lighting which beats to the rhythm of your music.

Name: LG Compact Sound Bar With Bluetooth Connectivity SK1-BK Black
Short description:
• Compact Design
  • Bluetooth Streaming
  • TV Remote Compatibility
Description:
Compact Design
Step up to bigger, better TV sound without adding big, bulky boxes. The SK1 sound bar has a classic, ideally proportioned design that practically disappears beneath most TVs, a pleasure for the eyes as well as the ears.

The Sound Bar for the Serious Watcher
Enjoy cinema-like audio with this high-performing sound bar. The action flows above and around you to complete your home theater.

Bluetooth
Prized for its range and reliability, convenient Bluetooth wireless connectivity easily links portable devices such as smartphones and tablets—as well as compatible televisions—to a speaker or sound bar.

TV Remote Compatibility

Name: Google Home Mini Smart Speaker Charcoal
Short description:
• Get hands-free help in any room with Google Home Mini. It's powered by the Google Assistant. You can ask it questions. Tell it to do things. It's your own personal Google.
  • Use your voice to quickly find information about the weather, news, sports and more.
  • Control your favourite music, movies and shows, using only your voice.
  • Get help around the house with things like your schedule, commute, travel information and more
  • Google Home Mini can even help you find a lost iPhone or Android phone and make phone calls to any personal contact or business.
  • Use your voice to control your compatible lights, thermostats and more. Google Home Mini works with more than 1,000 smart devices from over 150 popular brands.
  • Get personalised responses for everyone at home with voice recognition.
Description: The Google Home Mini Smart Assistant in chalk has everything a Smart Assistant device requires in a small package. The Mini is a smooth flat disk measuring about 4 inches in length and 1.5 inches in height. The top half is a 360 degree speaker that has hidden LED status lights to help communicate when the Mini is working or listening. The Mini has a single switch that will disable the always-on microphone, and a Micro USB port. It requires only a power supply and to be synced to your home Wi-Fi network. It also has Bluetooth support, and functions as a Chromecast device. It responds to all voice commands and will listen actively for the phrase “OK Google”, which will let it know to follow the next command. The Mini can, on request, search for answers online, set alarms and manage appointments, play music, and fetch news and weather information. The Mini can also identify individual voices, so two different people asking what the traffic is like on the way to work, for example, will receive personalized answers. The Mini can offer step by step instructions for recipes, repeating and going back to previous steps on request and it can translate individual words and phrases, convert currency or other units of measurement, do advanced math, and read audiobooks. If connected to other smart devices, it can be used to control them. If connected to a television, the Mini can be used to play movies and TV shows on request. If connected to smart bulbs or switches, it can turn lights on and off.

Name: Google Nest Mini 2nd Generation Chalk
Short description:
• Far-Field Voice Recognition Technology
  • Dual-Band Wi-Fi Connectivity
  • 1x 1.58" Driver for 360° Sound
  • Multi-User Capability
  • Wireless Audio Streaming via Wi-Fi
  • Works with the Google Assistant
Description:
Better sound, all around.
Music sounds bigger and richer on Nest Mini, with more power and bass. Ask your Google Assistant to play your favorite songs from Spotify, YouTube Music, and more.¹ Or stream music from your phone to Nest Mini.⁴

A little help with the Google Assistant.
Just ask and get the best of Google – weather, news, or almost anything. Set timers and alarms. And with Voice Match, you can hear your personalized schedule, commute times, reminders, and more.² So your day gets off to a good start.

Control your home with just your voice.
Dim the lights, pause the TV, or turn up the heat – all with your voice.³ Nest Mini works with thousands of compatible smart devices, like lights, thermostats, and TVs, from your favorite brands. Just say "Hey Google."

Thoughtfully designed for every room.
Nest Mini blends right into your home. It looks great on a nightstand, shelf, or countertop – even on the wall. Each color complements the entryway, living room, bedroom, or kitchen.

¹ Music subscriptions may be required.

² Voice Match requires additional setup and enrollment, and supports up to six users. When using Voice Match, keep in mind that a voice similar to yours, or a recording of your voice, could result in Google incorrectly recognizing someone else as you.

³ Compatible smart devices required.

⁴ Android phone or Chromecast-enabled apps on iOS required.

Description:
Sleek, compact and ultra slim design
This Official Huawei wireless charging pad has been designed to complement the unique product styling of Huawei's new handsets and as such is the perfect home or office charging solution for your phone. Not only does the charger save tangled cables from cluttering your desk space, but the pad actually looks aesthetically pleasing with its smooth contours and clean lines.

Features over-charging prevention
The Huawei Qi Wireless Charger prevents your smartphone from continuing to charge once the battery is full, providing a smarter, more efficient charging solution over traditional mains chargers. Additionally this charging pad protects your device against overcharging and overheating.

Ambient LED charging status indicator
The Huawei Wireless Charging Pad is a perfect fit with any wireless charging handset. Quick and simple to use, this official wireless charger also features an ambient LED display, which indicates your phone's charging status.

Compatible with all Qi-enabled smartphones
Any smartphone which has Qi wireless technology can utilise this pad's charging capabilities. If your phone doesn't have Qi, don't worry - we sell a range of adapters, one of which is sure to be perfect for your device.

Name: Bose Quiet Comfort Earbuds Black
Short description:
• built-in Bluetooth 5.1 for wireless music listening and phone calls with compatible smartphones
  • clear, spacious sound with deep bass
  • active noise cancellation uses internal circuitry to block out external distractions
  • earbud controls let you select high or low levels of cancellation, or "transparency mode" to hear external sounds
  • 11 discrete noise cancellation levels available via the mobile app
  • IPX4 sweat- and weather-resistant
Description:
Controls and mobile app:

touch controls on each earbud let you answer calls and control music, noise cancellation, and volume

access Siri or Google Assistant voice controls assistants from your phone

built-in microphone array for taking calls

mic system designed to better capture your voice in noisy or windy conditions

free, optional Bose® Music app for Apple and Android offers seamless toggling between multiple Bluetooth devices

customize your sound settings and noise cancellation

General information and accessories:
three sizes of soft silicone StayHear™ Max tips provide a stable, comfortable fit

flexible wings keep earbuds secure during exercise

extended wing redesign for better contact distribution that avoids pressure points

built-in rechargeable batteries offer up to 6 hours of listening with noise cancellation

voice prompts provide information on battery life, device connection, and caller ID

included carrying case banks up to 12 hours of power to wirelessly recharge headphones

15 minutes inside case provides enough power for 2 hours of listening with noise cancellation

Name: Bose Sport Earbuds Triple Black
Short description:
• Bose lifelike sound
  • Secure and comfortable earbuds
  • Weather and sweat resistant earbuds
  • Clear calls
  • Simple touch controls
  • Long battery life
  • Reliable Bluetooth connectivity
  • Bose Music app
Description:
Wireless Bluetooth earbuds engineered by Bose for your best workout yet.

Bose lifelike sound — makes your music sound like the performer is right there beside you, pushing you to go one more mile or do one more rep.

Secure and comfortable earbuds — customize your fit with the included 3 sizes of StayHear Max tips that won’t hurt your ears and won’t fall out no matter tough your workout is.

Weather and sweat resistant earbuds — IPX4 rated, with electronics wrapped in special materials to protect from moisture wherever you exercise

Clear calls — a beamforming microphone array separates your voice from surrounding noise so your callers can hear you better.

Simple touch controls — Instead of buttons, the capacitive touch interface lets you swipe up and down for volume control (opt in feature via Bose Music App), tap to play or pause music, answer calls, and more

Long battery life— up to 5 hours per charge with the included charging case, plus up to 2 more hours with a 15-minute quick charge on the go.

Reliable Bluetooth connectivity — custom-designed antennas hidden inside each earbud ensure dropouts are rare. Compatible with IOS & Android and has a Bluetooth range of 30 ft. (9 m)

Bose Music app — start by downloading the app and syncing your earbuds, then name your earbuds, set the controls, check battery life, and more.

Name: Bose Noise Cancelling Headphones NC700-BK Black
Short description:
• Comfortable Over-Ear Design
  • Bose AR Audio-Only Augmented Reality
  • Adaptive 4-Microphone System
  • 11 Levels of Noise Cancellation
Description:
Enjoy seamless integration into your mobile lifestyle with the triple black Bose Headphones 700 noise-canceling Bluetooth headphones. Utilize the built-in Google Assistant and Amazon Alexa combined with one-touch access to voice assistants for comprehensive, convenient, hands-free control of your smartphone functions, all while leaving your phone in your pocket. Through intuitive taps and gestures on the right earcup's touch surface, you can control functions such as answering/declining calls, adjusting volume, skipping tracks, and playing/pausing audio. Plus, the innovative Bose AR audio-only augmented reality function fluidly merges digital experiences with the physical world around you to enhance the way you travel, exercise, and more.

Thanks to the adaptive 4-microphone system, your voice will be picked up with clarity and consistency regardless of your location, so you won't have to waste time repeating voice commands or conversations with friends. 11 levels of noise cancellation and a special Conversation Mode allow you to decide exactly how much ambient sound you want to hear, whether you're working indoors at the office, flying to a remote destination, or walking through the city.

Active EQ sound management manipulates the sonic signature of the headphones to keep you immersed in your content at any listening volume. The sleek over-ear design features a lightweight, padded, stainless-steel headband and angled, rotating earcups, ensuring all-day comfort. With 20 hours of wireless battery life, you're likely to wear them from morning until night.

Adaptive 4-microphone system picks up and isolates your voice while cancelling the noise around you

Optimized for Google Assistant and Amazon Alexa; press a button on the right earcup to activate your chosen voice assistant

Manage tracks, volume, and phone calls with intuitive touch controls on the right earcup

Personalize the amount of ambient noise you wish to hear with 11 levels of noise cancellation plus Conversation Mode

For quick interruptions, press a button for Conversation Mode to pause the music and let surrounding noise in

Combining the power of wearable audio products, mobile devices, and integrated apps, Bose AR unlocks the potential to experience fundamentally new ways to travel, exercise, learn, play, and more by augmenting your world with content for your ears instead of your eyes

Enjoy an immersive listening experience at any volume with signature active EQ and plentiful bass response; whether you're listening at low volumes or really want to turn it up, your music sounds just as it should

Proprietary TriPort acoustic headphone structure utilizes external ports to vent the earcups and effectively enlarge the acoustic volume without increasing the size of the earcup, giving you better audio and active noise reduction from a smaller, lighter, more comfortable headphone

Stainless-steel headband with ultra-soft foam underside

Comfortable, angled earcups made from synthetic protein leather

From sound management to music management, the Bose Music app gives you even more control and ensures your Bose smart products work together for a better listening experience

Wireless or wired operation

Name: Bose Wireless Headphones QC35II-BK Black
Short description:
• Google Assistant / Amazon Alexa Button
  • Bluetooth Wireless with NFC Pairing
  • Three Levels of Noise Cancellation
  • Noise-Rejecting Dual Microphones
Description:
Styled in a sleek black color, the Bose QuietComfort 35 Series II are wireless noise-canceling headphones. These headphones differ from the original QuietComfort 35 headphones with the addition of a button on the left earcup. Press and hold it to speak to Google Assistant or Amazon Alexa when connected to your smart assistant-enabled device. Or, use it to change the level of noise cancellation between Full, Low, or Off.

The headphones can be paired with two devices at once via Bluetooth or NFC technology, and accept voice prompts in English, Spanish, Mandarin, or Dutch, with other languages available through Bose's website. The Bose Connect app, available on the Apple App Store and Google Play, allows you to switch between multiple Bluetooth-enabled devices easily, keeping your headphones digitally up to date at the same time.

These headphones feature active noise cancellation, as well as a noise-rejecting, dual-microphone system that renders phone calls clear even in windy or noisy situations. Its Sidetone feature allows you to hear your own voice, despite the noise reduction. With one 2.25-hour charge, these headphones can stream audio for up to 20 hours; using the included 3.5mm audio cable, the QuietComfort 35's noise-reduction capabilities will last for up to 40 hours before requiring recharging.

These headphones, with Alcantara earcups that rotate for safe storage, also sport volume-optimized EQ intended to maintain frequency balance across any output level, while their active noise cancellation mitigates unwelcome dins such as street sounds, airplane cabin noise, and more. The right earcup sports volume controls and a multi-function button, which can control play/pause, skip-track, rewind, fast-forward, and your phone's default voice assistant. In addition to the 4' 3.5mm audio cable, a carrying case and a 12" charging cable are also included.

Smart Assistant Compatible
The QuietComfort 35 Series II headphones give you the ability to interact with a variety of smart assistants. When paired with your mobile device, you can use the QuietComfort to talk to the device's native smart assistant, such as Bixby or Google Assistant on a Samsung Note9, or Siri on an iPhone X. It can also let you interact with Amazon Alexa via an additional app download. You can choose to use your QuietComfort 35 headphones with your preferred assistant, or take advantage of them all if you'd like. Heading out for the night? Use your QuietComfort 35 to have Alexa send a message to your friend's Echo that you're leaving, have Google Assistant launch directions to the party, and tell Siri to take a selfie with everyone when you arrive.

Name: Bose Speaker System S1PRO-BK Black
Short description:
• Rugged Lightweight PA System
  • Integrated Tone Match Processing
  • Multi-Positional Design(Monitor, Tripod, Tilt Back)
  • Built in 3 channel mixer with reverb and EQ controls
  • Bluetooth For Wireless Music Streaming
Description: The Bose S1 Pro is a portable PA System that provides high quality portable sound for DJ's, Musicians, and performers. It's exceptionally lightweight design, built in 3 channel Bluetooth equipped mixer, and innovative Auto-EQ technology deliver incredible versatility allowing you to get high quality sound in any location. Lightweight high quality PA System, weighing just over 15lbs, the S1 Pro lets you take high definition audio on the road. The sleek cabinet is ultra rugged and is designed with a built in convenient carry handle for quick set up and breakdown. An optional rechargeable Lithium Ion Battery (Sold Separately) lets you optimize the speaker for outdoor use and other locations where access to power is limited.Built in 3 channel mixer with Bluetooth.\n\nThe S1 Pro includes a dedicated 3 channel mixer for integrating multiple participants and music sources into your performance. Channels 1 2 offer XLR_1/4 combo inputs with bass and treble EQ and selectable reverb level. Channel 3 includes a 3.5mm stereo input and Bluetooth so you can wirelessly stream music from your smartphone, tablet or laptop. The mixer also features a line output for combining multiple S1 Pro systems.Multiple positions with Auto-EQ. The S1 Pro cabinet is designed for maximum performance flexibility. Use it as a stage monitor, mount it on a speaker stand, or tilt it back to experiment with a different bass response. Bose proprietary Auto EQ automatically optimizes the speakers response based on positioning. This allows you to setup quickly and focus completely on your performance.

Name: Sony True Wireless With Noise Cancelation Black
Short description:
• Simultaneous Streaming to Both Earbuds
  • Support for Google Assistant
  • Bluetooth 5.0 Technology
  • Built-In Mic for Hands-Free Calling
  • Tri-Hold Design & Anti-Friction Rubber
Description:
Engineered to provide you with complete audio freedom without distraction, WF-1000XM3 True Wireless Noise-Canceling In-Ear Earphones from Sony incorporates sophisticated noise-canceling technologies to isolate you with only your favorite music, TV shows, podcasts, or other audio entertainment. The 1000XM3 earphones utilizes forward- and rear-facing microphones to take in distracting ambient sounds and noises, and Sony's QN1e HD noise-canceling processor works to completely filter them out.

Thanks to DSEE HX technology, your compressed digital files are upscaled to get them close to high-resolution quality. This audio is transmitted via Bluetooth from your nearby mobile device and the built-in Bluetooth chip is designed to keep signals solid and in sync. Made to stay secure in your ears, these wireless earphones can work all day long with up to 8 hours of battery life, and another 24 from the handy magnetic charging case.

Optimized Bluetooth Technology
The integrated Bluetooth antenna has been constructed to help provide a wider range of coverage, and when that audio is received, the integrated Bluetooth chip supports simultaneous transmission to both earbuds. The chip is also made to help keep audio in sync with the video on your device's screen, and provide a stable connection for hours.

Secure & Comfortable Fit
The ergonomically designed earbuds have been fashioned with a tri-hold structure that makes contact with your ears via three different points, helping to keep everything secure and comfortable. Added security is provided by a high-friction rubber surface that covers sections of both earbuds.

Magnetic Charging Case Included
When you're ready to put away these truly wireless earbuds, simply snap them into the included magnetic charging case. The earphones stay protected and recharge all at once. The earbuds can provide up to 6 hours of battery life with noise cancelling turned on, and the case can give you three more charges for a total of 24 hours of use. If you shut off noise cancellation, the earbuds can last for 8 hours alone, and 32 hours overall with the case.

Quick Attention
Touch the outside of the earbud to automatically turn down the volume so you can have a quick conversation or hear an announcement.

Sony Headphones Connect App
Adaptive Sound Control: Automatically detects what you're doing, such as walking, traveling, or waiting, and auto-adjusts your ambient sound settings to suit the situation. The app also lets you customize these settings to your liking.
Ambient Sound Control: Adjust the volume of background sound or only allow voices to be heard.
Equalizer: Customize your sound levels to suit your style of music.
Customize Controls: The app allows you to customize the default touch controls and assign alternative functions, like activating Google Assistant.

Hands-Free Calling
A built-in microphone within the earbuds allows you to make hands-free calls when paired with a smartphone. The feature works with either one or both earbuds inserted.

Additional Smart Features
Automatically pause playback by removing an earbud and resume by putting it back in
Supports Google Assistant for getting information and notifications, asking questions, setting reminders and more
Touch controls in both earbuds to control noise cancellation and audio playback

  • Truly wireless design with BLUETOOTH wireless technology
  • 9-hour long battery life, total 18-hour with charging case
  • Ergonomic design for a secure, comfortable fit

Description:
Bring EXTRA BASS™ to everything you do, truly wireless style meets deep, punchy EXTRA BASS sound. Enhance your everyday life with the WF-XB700. Boost your vibes

Name: Sony Wireless Noise Cancelling Stereo Headphone Black
Short description:
• Custom Sound for Activities & Locations
  • Wearing Detection & Speak-to-Chat
  • Hi-Res Audio Compatible 1.57" Drivers
  • Built-In Rechargeable Battery
  • LDAC, AAC, and SBC Wireless Codecs
  • Automatically Adjusts Ambient Sound
  • DSEE Extreme Audio Upscaling
  • Wireless Bluetooth & NFC Tap Technology
  • Up to 30 Hours of Playback with BT+ANC
  • Includes 3.5mm Audio Cable
Description:
No matter where you go, the black Sony WH-1000XM4 Wireless Noise-Canceling Over-Ear Headphones deliver pristine sound quality while automatically adjusting ambient sound according to your activity and registered locations, leaving your hands and mind free from the hassle of changing settings just to hear what you want to hear. Plus, the headphones detect when you're wearing them and start and stop your audio for you.

Noise cancellation is accomplished with Sony's dedicated HD Noise-Canceling QN1 processor and Sense Engine. Sense Engine is designed to automatically adjust the level of ambient sound based on your environment. If quick communication is needed, simply speak to chat without audio playing or just cover the right earcup with your hand to monitor the outside world.

When it comes to what you do hear, the WH-1000XM4 headphones use DSEE Extreme audio upscaling to perform genre- and instrument-based optimization of the sound, and they support LDAC, AAC, and SBC codecs. When used with a compatible source device, LDAC transmits approximately three times more data, up to 990 kb/s, compared to conventional Bluetooth. This is meant to make your high-resolution audio content sound even better when it's played back through the 1.57" drivers with LCP diaphragms (liquid crystal polymer).

Whether you're looking for peace and quiet while working from home or you want an ideal pair of headphones for traveling, Sony crafted the noise-canceling WH-1000XM4 to be both convenient (with support for Alexa, Siri, and Google Assistant) and comfortable, thanks to the soft, pressure-relieving earpads and the lightweight design.

High-Tech Noise Cancellation
Dual noise sensor technology, featuring two microphones on each earcup, captures ambient noise and passes the data to the HD Noise Canceling Processor QN1. Using a new algorithm, the HD Noise-Canceling Processor QN1 then applies noise cancellation processing in real time to a range of acoustic environments.

Working together with a new Bluetooth Audio SoC (system on chip), it senses and adjusts to music and noise signals, as well as acoustic characteristics between the driver unit and ears, at over 700 times per second.
Adaptive Sound Control
Adaptive Sound Control is a smart function that can learn to recognize locations you frequently visit, such as your workplace or favorite café, and tailor sound for the ideal listening experience. In addition, it automatically detects what you're up to—walking, waiting or traveling—then adjusts ambient sound settings to suit the situation.
Optimized Noise Canceling
The WH-1000XM4 headphones incorporate two technologies to maximize noise-canceling performance. Unique Atmospheric Pressure Optimizing delivers optimal sound at high altitude, while Personal Noise Cancellation Optimizer analyzes unique sonic characteristics caused by head size, glasses, and hair, then tailors sound to you.
Wearing Detection
A proximity sensor in the WH-1000XM4 headphones can detect whether you're wearing them or not, then adapt playback accordingly to help save battery power. Take off your headphones and the music pauses automatically. Put the headphones back on and the music automatically resumes.
Speak-to-Chat Convenience
As soon as you speak to someone, Speak-to-Chat automatically stops the music and lets in ambient sound so you can conduct a conversation—handy if you want to keep your headphones on or your hands are full. Based on Precise Voice Pickup Technology, this smart feature uses five microphones built into the headphones and advanced audio signal processing to recognize and react to your voice. Once your chat is over, your music starts playing again automatically.
Quick Attention
Regardless of the level of noise-cancelation, the Quick Attention features lets you quickly hear your environment, whether it's to hear an emergency announcement or have a quick conversation. Simply place your hand over the housing of the right earcup to quiet things down so you can hear.
Sony Headphones Connect App
Adjust ambient sound with the Sony | Headphones Connect app to cancel noise while still allowing essential sounds, like transport announcements, through when you're listening on the move. Ambient Sound Control lets you adjust the volume of background sound and gives you the option to allow voices alone to be heard. Meanwhile the Equalizer lets you customize sound levels to suit your music.
Voice Assistant Integration
When the WH-1000XM4 headphones are paired with your smartphone, you can use them to access the phone's voice assistant. Ask it questions and have it perform tasks just like you would normally do; enjoy entertainment, connect with friends, get information, listen to music and notifications, set reminders, and more.
Hands-Free Calling
Conversation flows freely with easy, hands-free calling. Leave your phone where it is, just speak with a double tap. Thanks to Precise Voice Pickup Technology, which combines five built-in microphones with advanced audio signal processing, WH-1000XM4 delivers clearer voice quality to the other person on the phone.
Hi-Res Audio
A built-in analog amplifier integrated in the HD Noise-Canceling Processor QN1 realizes a pristine signal-to-noise ratio for low distortion and exceptional sound quality for portable devices. Powerful 1.57" drivers with liquid crystal polymer (LCP) diaphragms make the headphones ideal for handling heavy beats, and they can also reproduce a full range of frequencies up to 40 kHz.
DSEE Extreme Audio Upscaling
Using Edge-AI (Artificial Intelligence) co-developed with Sony Music Entertainment, DSEE Extreme (Digital Sound Enhancement Engine) upscales compressed digital music files in real time. Dynamically recognizing instrumentation, musical genres, and individual elements of each song, such as vocals or interludes, it restores the high-range sound lost in compression for a richer, more complete listening experience.
Multipoint Connection
For total convenience, WH-1000XM4 headphones can be paired with two Bluetooth devices at the same time. When a call comes in, your headphones know which device is ringing and connect to the right one automatically. You'll also be able to quickly and smoothly switch your headphones to either of the two devices at the touch of a button.
Additional Features
Battery Life: Up to 30 hours of playback with active noise cancellation
Quick Charge: With just 10 minutes of charging via an AC adapter (not included), you can gain up to 5 hours of battery life
Tap Controls: Intuitive tap and swipe gestures on the outside of the right earcup let you adjust volume, play/pause audio, change tracks, and answer calls
Swivel & Foldable: The earcups swivel inwards so they pack up neatly in the included compact case
