When used with a compatible source device, LDAC transmits approximately three times more data, up to 990 kb/s, compared to conventional Bluetooth. This is meant to make your high-resolution audio content sound even better when it's played back through the 1.57" drivers with LCP diaphragms (Liquid Crystal Polymer).

Whether you're just looking for peace and quiet or a quiet listening experience, Sony crafted these noise-canceling headphones to be comfortable while wearing them. The earpads are made from soft, pressure-relieving foam urethane, and an overall lightweight design that comes in at only 9 oz.

Sense Engine and Adaptive Sound Control
Sony's Sense Engine and Adaptive Sound Control technology are designed give you a smarter set of noise-canceling headphones. They automatically adjust the level of cancellation based on your activity.

If walking or waiting, they will adjust to help you be aware of your surroundings and hear announcements. While traveling, it adjusts to help keep you from being disturbed. When flying, unique atmospheric pressure optimizing adjusts to help deliver optimal sound at high altitudes.
Personalized Noise-Canceling Optimization
The Personal NC Optimizer is designed to adjust itself based on head size, hair type, and whether you're wearing glasses.
Quick Attention
Regardless of the level of noise-cancelation, the Quick Attention features lets you quickly hear your environment, whether it's to hear an emergency announcement or have a quick conversation. Simply place your hand over the housing of the right earcup to quiet things down so you can hear.

The WH-1000XM3 headphones can be controlled via the Sony | Headphones Connect app for iOS and Android devices. With it you can adjust the equalizer and noise cancellation settings to customize your listening experience.
Voice Assistant
When the WH-1000XM3 headphones are paired with your smartphone, you can use them to access the phone's voice assistant. Ask it questions and have it perform tasks just like you would normally do.
Hands-Free Calling
With a simple double tap of the earcup, you can answer incoming calls when paired with your phone. Multiple microphones are built in to help give you clear call quality.
Additional Features
Battery Life: Up to 30 hours of playback with active noise cancellation
Quick Charge: With just 10 minutes of charging via an AC adapter (not included), you can gain up to 5 hours of battery life
Tap Controls: Intuitive tap and swipe gestures on the outside of the right earcup let you adjust volume, play/pause audio, change tracks, and answer calls
Virtual Surround Sound: Experience audio optimized for different listening environments, such as outdoor stages, clubs, halls, and arenas
Sound Position Control: Choose the direction you want the sound to come from, just as you can with a wireless speaker
Swivel & Foldable: The earcups swivel inwards so they pack up neatly in the included compact case

Name: Sony Over-Ear Bluetooth Headphone With Noise Cancelation Black
Short description:
• 30mm Drivers
  • Active Noise Cancellation
  • Support for Hands-Free Calling
  • One-Touch NFC Bluetooth Pairing
  • Adjustable Headband
  • Up to 35 Hours of Battery Life
  • Access to Digital Assistants
  • Ambient Sound Mode
  • Large, Cushioned Oval Earcups
  • Folds Flat for Easy Travel
Description:
Isolate yourself from the world around you with these WH-CH710N Noise-Canceling Wireless Over-Ear Headphones from Sony. Utilizing a forward- and backward-facing microphone, the CH710N headphones actively cancel out distracting ambient noise, leaving you to focus on your favorite audio. When you need to hear outside sounds, simply turn on Ambient Sound mode to listen to music while still being able to hear traffic, announcements, and more.

Powering these over-ear headphones are 30mm drivers that can reproduce the full range of audio frequencies. Audio is streamed via Bluetooth-compatible mobile devices, and pairing is made simple with support for NFC technology. With up to 35 hours of playback you can enjoy these Sony noise-canceling headphones for hours on end. Sony provided comfort features to help make wearing them a pleasant experience. The headband is fully adjustable and the large oval earcups each have soft cushions.

Digital Assistants & Hands-Free Calls
Built-in microphones provide additional features when paired with a smartphone or other digital assistant-equipped device. With access to digital assistants, you can get answers to questions, step-by-step navigation, manage your music, and much more by just using your voice. Pair the over-ear headphones with a smartphone and also enjoy the ability to make hands-free calls.
NFC Pairing
Manual Bluetooth pairing is supported, but with NFC pairing, you can more quickly use these headphones with your devices. To pair, simply tap your NFC-enabled device to the N-mark logo on the headphones.
Quick Charge
In a hurry? Charge the headphones for just 10 minutes to enjoy up to an hour of playback.

Description:
With the WH-XB900N Wireless Active Noise-Canceling Over-Ear Headphones from Sony, you can experience your favorite albums or podcasts without the distracting sounds around you. A single microphone takes in the ambient noise, such as traffic noise or people talking, and neutralizes them so all you hear is what you're playing.

The XB900N headphones are engineered to enhance the audio you ear with EXTRA BASS technology. It utilizes a dedicated bass duct on the headphone's housing to give an extra boost to your music, without affecting vocal clarity. The WH-XB900N over-ear headphones are designed to last for up to 30 hours, for all-day entertainment, and can pair to your mobile device via Bluetooth or NFC. Other features include touch controls, digital assistant access, and more.

Convenient and Comfortable Design
These XB900N wireless headphones have soft cushioned earpads to help make them comfortable during extended listening. They are also foldable for easier storage, which helps to make them an ideal fit as your everyday carry headphones.
Hands-Free Calling
A built-in microphone inside the headphones lets you have hands-free phone calls when they are paired with your smartphone. The earcup touch controls let you answer calls and adjust the volume.
Earcup Touch Controls with Quick Attention
The exterior of the right earcup features a built-in touch panel that gives you touch control over volume, music playback, hands-free calls, and the Quick Attention feature. Quick Attention is a useful feature that's enabled by simply placing your hand on the earcup. The volume will automatically lower, allowing you to have a quick conversation or listen to the world around you, all without having to take off your headphones.
Google Assistant & Alexa
The Sony XB900 headphones support both Google Assistant and Alexa digital assistants. Via the headphone's built-in mic, you can ask questions, receive notifications, set reminders, and more.
Sony Headphones Connect App
The XB900N headphones are made to work with Sony's Headphones Connect app, which lets you customize your listening experience via your mobile device. A built-in equalizer lets you adjust sound levels, and Adaptive Sound Control automatically adjusts the ambient sound settings to suit your specific situation

The volume will automatically lower, allowing you to have a quick conversation or listen to the world around you, all without having to take off your headphones.
Google Assistant & Alexa
The Sony XB900 headphones support both Google Assistant and Alexa digital assistants. Via the headphone's built-in mic, you can ask questions, receive notifications, set reminders, and more.
Sony Headphones Connect App
The XB900N headphones are made to work with Sony's Headphones Connect app, which lets you customize your listening experience via your mobile device. A built-in equalizer lets you adjust sound levels, and Adaptive Sound Control automatically adjusts the ambient sound settings to suit your specific situation

Name: Sony On-Ear Bluetooth Headphone Black

• 30mm Closed Dynamic Drivers
  • Built-In Mic for Hands-Free Calling
  • Wireless Bluetooth 5.0 Technology
  • Swivel Earcups for Increased Portability
  • Up to 35 Hours of Playback
  • Supports Smartphone Voice Assistants
  • Quick Charge Support
Description:
Enjoy multi-day audio entertainment with the WH-CH510 Wireless On-Ear Headphones from Sony. These on-ear headphones provide up to 35 hours of continuous playback of your favorite music, podcasts, and more. Audio is pumped through 30mm closed dynamic drivers and streamed wirelessly from your mobile devices via Bluetooth 5.0 technology. If you pair the WH-CH510 headphones with your smartphone, you can also use the built-in mic for hands-free calls. The built-in mic can also be used with your smartphone's voice assistant by double-pressing the Play button, giving you access to asking your device questions, getting step-by-step navigation, playing media, setting reminders, and much more.

Additional Features
Swivel earcups help to make the WH-CH510 headphones more portable
Built-in playback controls on the earcup
10 minutes of quick charge provides up to 90 minutes of playback

Name: Sony Portable Bluetooth Speaker Black
Short description:
• Stereo Male Audio Cable
  • EXTRA BASS PORTABLE SPEAKER: Its small and compact design with Bluetooth connectivity makes it easy to take anywhere and allows for quick connection
  • BUILT IN MIC AND HANDY STRAP: With the built-in microphone, you taking calls from your smartphone via the speaker is easy. The handy strap comes in a matching color and secures your speaker anywhere
  • PLAYBACK: If you don't have wireless connections, no worry, with the audio input you can connect your music players and enjoy your favorite playlists
Description:
Take your party on the go with the Sony XB01 Extra Bass Portable Bluetooth Speaker. Its small and compact design with Bluetooth connectivity makes it easy to take anywhere and allows for quick connection. No wireless connection? You can still have your party. Just attach your device with an audio cable thanks to the speaker's audio input. Extra Bass technology will get the bass pumping for a rocking party!

Compact Design

The SRS-XB01 features a rounded design and passive radiator that give your tunes deep and punchy sound. Despite its compact size, this speaker delivers a big sound.

Built-in Microphone

Hands-free calling lets you switch quickly from tunes to talking with friends. With the built-in microphone, taking calls from your smartphone via the speaker is easy.

Handy Strap

With the SRS-XB01's handy strap, you're never separated from your favorite tracks. It comes in a matching color and secures your speaker anywhere.

Playback Through Audio Input

No wireless connection? No problem. Plug your music player, such as Walkman or iPod, into the SRS-XB01's audio input and enjoy your favorite playlists.

Bundle Includes:

Sony XB01 Extra Bass Portable Bluetooth Speaker (Black)
Monoprice 10-Feet 3.5mm Stereo Male to 3.5mm Stereo Male Audio Cable (Gold Plated)

Name: Sony Portable Bluetooth Speaker With Xtra Bass Black
Short description:
• MUSIC THAT TRAVELS: Small size but mighty in volume to deliver powerful beats wherever you travel
  • VIRTUAL HAPPY HOUR: Turn your virtual happy hour party into a dance party with EXTRA BASS, and pair two for even more fun
  • PERFECTLY PORTABLE: Use the detachable carry strap to hang, carry, or clip the speaker to your bag
  • WATERPROOF CASING: Take to the pool or beach without worrying about water damaging the speaker unit
  • TOTALLY DUSTPROOF: This outdoor pocket speaker will keep on playing no matter how dusty the surface
  • UPGRADE THE AUDIO: Wirelessly connect 2 speakers and achieve stereo sound with Speaker Add Function
  • LONGER BATTERY LIFE: Party for longer with this rechargeable speaker's extended 16 hour battery life
  • COMPACT SIZE: Measures approx. 3” in diameter and 3 5/8” in height and only weighs approx. 8. 6 oz
  • PLAY ANYWHERE: Full range speaker for use at home, in your car, on a bike, while hiking, and more
Description:
Bring your music to life with EXTRA BASS
Get things going with EXTRA BASS. A passive radiator works with the monaural speaker to enhance low-end tones, giving bass a boost despite the compact size.

Dustproof Design
With an IP67 rating, you can take your speaker to the trail, the forest, the city, or wherever you like - the XB12 will keep on playing, no matter how dusty the surface.

Waterproof Design
With an IP67 rating, your speaker can withstand being in and around water.

Up to 16 hours of battery life
Listen for longer with up to 16 hours of battery life.

Small and light design
The XB12 is compact, wireless, and made to go with you anywhere. With the included detachable strap, you can hang or carry it anywhere and keep your music going on the move.

Add an extra speaker for stereo sound
Simply connect two speakers wirelessly for stereo sound.

Name: Sony Hifi Party Speaker Black
Short description:
• Powerful sound and jet bass booster for room filling bass
  • Multi source playback (Bluetooth/NFC, CD, DVD, USB, etc.) & Easy connection to TV via HDMI
  • Versatile operation modes with gesture control, the Sony | music centre app or voice control via the Fiestable app
  • Multi-colour party lights & Speaker lights that synchronize to the beat
  • Karaoke mode with two mic inputs
Description: Get the party started with Sony’s MHC-V42D sound system. Whatever the occasion, the V42D will fill your space with big volume and booming bass. With angled tweeters spreading sound wider and the JET BASS BOOSTER ensuring bass reaches every corner, wherever you are in the crowd you will hear it clearly and feel it physically. You can also create an immersive festival vibe with the Live Sound Mode which floods your party space with the realistic sound of a live concert. With Near Field Communication (NFC) and Bluetooth, you can connect wirelessly to the high power audio system and get the music going right away. You’ll also benefit from Sony’s LDAC technology, which delivers superior-quality sound over Bluetooth. With different operation modes, you can control your party your way. Gesture Control lets you control the Sony MHC V42D’s functions quickly and easily with just a wave of your hand. The Sony | Music Centre app lets you select the tunes from the dancefloor. You can even connect up to three smartphones at once, so everyone can take turns as the DJ. Voice Control via the Fiestable app allows you to simply say the word and control your music and light display. Light up every corner of the party, even in large spaces with new wider angle multi-coloured party lights and speaker lights that synchronize to the beat, so you can enjoy an authentic nightclub or outdoor festival atmosphere at home. Plus you can get the crowd involved with the Fiestable smartphone app, which turns your smartphone display into your very own party light, mirroring the sound system’s colours and effects. Free your inner pop star with Sony MHCV42D’s karaoke mode. Use the two mic inputs to sing along with friends or even hook up a guitar or bass guitar and rock out. Boost the party and enjoy more powerful sound by connecting multiple speakers via Bluetooth. You can sync up to 50 compatible home audio systems. Not in the mood for dancing? Then throw a movie party. With the HDMI (ARC) output, you can easily hook the sound system up to your TV and enjoy big sound from your top films. The Sony MHC-V42D has even a built-in DVD player, so you can turn your living room into a cinema for you and your friends. Designed for portability, the party sound system lets you take the party on tour. Simply tilt it back on the casters and roll it away to your next stop.

Name: Fitbit Versa 2 Fitness Wristband Stone/Mist Grey
Short description:
• Aluminium Case
  • Track your steps, monitor your heart rate and more!
  • Always-On Display Mode
  • Compatible with Android and iOS Smartphones
  • Water resistant to 50 metres.
Description:
Let your voice be heard with Amazon Alexa
Just press the button and speak to check the weather, set reminders, get on-screen answers to your questions and more using Amazon Alexa.

Sleep better, live better
Sleep plays a huge role in your health. Wear Versa 2 at night to learn about your sleep, develop better habits and wake up ready to take on the world.

Focus on your health and fitness
That extra push you need to get going? It’s just a glance away. Versa 2 uses heart rate, guidance and insights to help you reach your goals.

Access your world from your wrist
Stick to your schedule, queue up the perfect playlist, make purchases & more—all from the convenience of your smartwatch.

Know your body better in the Fitbit app.
See the whole picture by using Versa 2 with the free Fitbit app to get the data, motivation and guidance you need to improve.

Name: Fitbit Versa 3 Fitness Wristband Black
Short description:
• Over 6 Days of Battery Life
  • 24/7 Heart Rate Monitoring
  • Stream or Store & Play Music/Podcasts
  • Swimproof Construction
  • SmartTrack Automatic Activity Detection
  • Built-In GPS Tracking
  • Track the Quality of Your Sleep
  • All-Day Activity Tracking
  • Female Health Tracking
  • Call, Text & App Notifications
Description:
More easily track your outdoor exercises with the Versa 3 GPS Smartwatch from Fitbit Made for multi-day tracking the Versa 3 features over 6 days of battery life and utilizes built-in GPS tracking, so you don't need to bring your smartphone along on a run, hike, or while biking. The GPS function tracks both your pack and distance. The Versa 3 handles a variety of exercises and basic 24/7 activity tracking of steps, distance, and calories burned. You can choose from over 20 exercises to track, or use SmartTrack, where the Versa 3 will automatically detect the exercise and track it for you.

Your health is intimately linked with how effective you are in reaching your fitness goals. With the Versa 3, you get 24/7 heart rate monitors that earns you Active Zone Minutes when reaching target heart rate zones. You can even keep tabs on your sleep quality by wearing it through the night. You can learn how well you've slept, get an overall sleep score, and learn about sleep trends that you can adjust for a better night's rest. All of these features and more are can be controlled via the Versa 3's built-in bright OLED display.

Manage Your Music
When you do bring your smartphone with you, you can use the Versa 3's built-in apps to manage a variety of audio experiences to keep you motivated. Access Spotify, download Pandora stations, or play Deezer playlists.

Notifications & Assistants
Pairing with iOS and Android devices gives you additional practical features to keep you connected to the outside world. Receive incoming calls, texts, and app notifications. You can also perform functions and get information using voice commands. The Versa 3 supports both Google Assistant and Alexa digital assistants.

Health Features
Uses PurePulse 2.0 to record your resting heart rate
Track calories burned, view heart rate trends and cardio fitness levels in the Fitbit app
See how much light, deep, and REM sleep you get
Smart Wake gives you a quiet vibration to more peacefully wake you
Sleep Mode disables notifications to help you sleep better
Personalized 2- and 5-minute guided breathing sessions based on your heart rate
Women can track menstrual cycles, record symptoms, and more
Personalized reminders nudge you to move more, keep to a regular sleep schedule, take 250 steps per hour, and more

Fitness Features
Use the Fitbit app to view a workout intensity map, seeing heart rate zones reached throughout your route
All-day activity tracking of steps, distance, floors climbed, active minutes, and calories burned
Wear the Versa 3 in the pool with up to 164' of water resistance
An in-app cardio fitness score gives you a better idea of your personal fitness level

Smart Features
Receive call, text, and app notifications
Android users can send quick replies to message from the Versa 3
Use the Fitbit app and Fitbit Pay to pay for items with a tap of your watch
Choose from hundreds of apps that cover many aspects of your daily life, such as Uber, United Airlines, TRX, and more
Do Not Disturb mode mutes calls, texts, calendar and app notifications

General Features
Get up to 24 hours of power in just 12 minutes with fast charging
The always-on display function lets you monitor your stats with just a glance
Customize the display with hundreds of clock face options online
Store up to 5 clock faces on the Versa 3
Compatible with the Fitbit app for viewing stats, taking part in group challenges, and much more
Categories: Smart Watches, Smart Watches > Smart Watches

Name: Belkin Powerhouse Charging Dock Duo Black
Short description:
• Back panel supports iPhone while charging
  • Includes a built-in Lightning connector for iPhone
  • Holds Apple Watch safely above surface
  • Versa Case- red dial raises/lowers adjustable case-friendly Lightning connector to fit most cases
  • Includes a built-in Magnetic Charging Module for Apple Watch
Description: Charge and display your Apple Watch and iPhone simultaneously with the 2-in-1 Powerhouse Charge Dock for Apple Watch plus iPhone. With a Magnetic Charging Module for the Apple Watch built into the dock, your Apple Watch aligns magnetically and begins charging instantly. The dock also features a built-in Versa Case Lightning connector to charge your iPhone, that can be adjusted to fit almost any case. Engineered to charge both devices at the fastest possible speed, the dock also elevates them for safety and visibility while they charge.

Name: Belkin 10000Mah Multi-Port Power Bank 15W White
Short description:
• 10,000mAh Battery Capacity
  • 1 x USB Type-C Input & Output
  • Up to 15W of Power Output
  • Portable Design
  • 6" USB Type-A to Type-C Cable Included
  • 2 x USB Type-A Output
  • 1 x Micro-USB Input
  • Charge up to Three Devices at Once
  • LED Indicator
Description:
Keep your gear juiced up on the go with the 10,000mAh Boost Charge Multi-Port Power Bank in white from Belkin. Designed to charge multiple devices at once, this power bank features two USB Type-A outputs, a USB Type-C input and output, and a micro-USB input. The 10,000mAh battery capacity and up to 15W of power delivery ensure your smartphone or other devices stay ready for use. An LED indicator alerts you to the charging status, and the Boost Charge Multi-Port is less than 4" on its longest side, making for easy transport. This power bank comes with a 6" USB Type-A to Type-C charging cable.

You Have the Power
The 10,000mAh Belkin Boost Charge Multi-Port provides up to 36 hours of battery life to your smartphone. Connect your device via USB Type-C or A, and you'll be able to chat, FaceTime, and use apps longer without having to worry about losing your charge.
Versatile Power
This power bank provides up to 15W of power when using the USB Type-C port, or when using all three ports. Get up to 12W of power when using a single USB Type-A port, or up to 12W shared when using both Type-A ports.

Name: Belkin Power Pocket 15000Mah With 2 Usb Ports Black
Short description:
• Compact and thin design for portability
  • 6 inch Micro-USB cable recharges the battery
  • 4 LED indicators show battery power level
  • Lightweight, efficient, Polymer cells
  • Durable plastic casing
Description:
Stay charged anywhere with the Belkin Pocket Power Bank 15000mAh w/ Micro USB Black that fits easily into your bag.

Two universal USB-A ports deliver up to 3.4A of total power to quickly and safely charge devices like smartphones, smartwatches, fitness bands, headphones, speakers and more.

Dual USB ports allow you to charge two devices at the same time, so you never have to choose between using your phone or tablet, camera or speakers, or anything else you need.

A 5V 2.0A input allows the power bank to recharge quickly between uses, so you can keep moving. 15,000 mAh recharges a smartphone to provide 105 additional hours of video playback.

Belkin batteries include sensors to monitor heat, voltage and circuitry so the device won’t overheat or surge. Excess heat, voltage fluctuation or circuit abnormalities activate an override that immediately shuts the battery down and keeps your devices safe.

Name: Belkin Usb 2.0 Travel Hub White
Short description:
• Adds four additional USB ports to your computer
  • Built-in cable management
  • Plug and play; no drivers required
  • Data transfer speeds of up to 480Mbps
  • Mac/PC compatible
Description: Enjoy the convenience of connecting four devices to a single USB hub with the this Belkin 4 port hub USB. You can connect various PC accessories to your PC or laptop and even charge multiple smartphones via this USB hub. It comes with an inbuilt plug-and-play functionality that allows you to connect and access USB devices without installing any software. Connect devices like flash drives or hard drives to this 4 port mini hub USB and transfer data at a high speeds of up to 480mbps.\n\nThis Belkin 4 port USB 2.0 hub is compatible with both 1.1 and 2.0 USB connectors, giving you the flexibility to connect myriad USB devices. Compact and lightweight, you can easily tuck it in your laptop bag or your satchel and get a move on. With this easy and multi-connectivity option, you can reduce the clutter of USB cables on your desktop too. With no extra power-supply requirement, this Belkin 4 port USB 2.0 hub is a handy accessory. Moreover, this ultra mini hub USB features a light indicator that flashes to signal connectivity.

  • 15cm length

AS SEEN ON SCREEN
From the screen of your USB-C-enabled device straight to your projector or monitor, smoothly and effortlessly. The USB-C to VGA Adapter is 15cm of finely tuned USB-C cable designed and tested by Belkin, allowing a seamless connection from any compatible USB-C device to your legacy projector, TV or monitor. Whether it’s sharing content at work, or transitioning new tech into your home office, it’s the ideal solution for your USB-C enabled device.

USB-C devices

Name: Belkin Usb-C To Gigabit Ethernet 60W Black
Short description:
• Plug-and-play USB-C to Ethernet adapter that allows for device charging
  • Charge while your device is in use with pass-through power up to 60W
  • Supports Ethernet speeds up to 1000 Mbps
  • Compatible with Mac and Windows laptops and other USB-C devices
  • Compatible devices: Any USB-C devices
Description:
Do It All Through One Port
Belkin USB-C to Ethernet + Charge Adapter
This USB-C to Ethernet + Charge Adapter provides convenient access to fast and reliable Internet connection through a gigabit Ethernet port and allows for USB Power Delivery at the same time. It's a plug-and-play adapter that works universally with Mac and Windows laptops and other USB-C devices.

Don't Stop to Charge
Connect and stay powered while surfing the Internet or transferring data. Pass-through Power Delivery of up to 60W allows you to stay charged while you work using a single USB-C port.

Reliable Ethernet Connection
Connect with confidence where wireless connectivity is inconsistent or even non-existent. This adapter provides access to a reliable Internet connection up to gigabit speeds up to 1000 Mbps for confidently transferring large files or hosting a web conference call without interruption.

Name: Belkin Lightning Audio + Charge Rockstar White
Short description:
• Metal shield provides structure to protect delicate circuit board
  • Shield prevents electro-magnetic interference from circuit board affecting phone signal and wifi
  • Electrical firmware design makes connectors interchangeable for audio and charging
  • MFi certified Lightning connectors carry audio and power
  • Jacket and strain relief made from flexible, soft touch, environmentally friendly TPE
Description:
DUAL FUNCTIONALITY
12W pass-through charging powers up the iPhone/iPad at maximum speed. So whether you’re listening to music, watching videos, using navigation, or taking calls, you can charge anywhere

AUDIO QUALITY
The Lightning Audio + Charge RockStar supports up to 24bit 48kHz lossless output, and is compatible with the full ecosystem of Lightning Audio headphones. The RockStar will also support the higher power delivery required by premium or professional standard Lightning Audio headphones to deliver superior noise cancellation without the need for batteries or an additional power supply.

"MADE FOR IPHONE" "MADE FOR IPAD"
“Made for iPhone” and “Made for iPad” mean that an electronic accessory has been designed to connect specifically to iPhone or iPad respectively, and has been certified by the developer to meet Apple specifications.

At A Glance:
Dual functionality to listen to Lightning Audio and charge at the same time

Supports pass-through charging up to 12W for iPhone and iPad

Supports up to 48 kHz, 24-bit audio output

Compatible with Lightning Audio headphones† and the Apple Lightning to 3.5 mm Headphone Jack Adapter

Supports remote control and microphone from Lightning Audio headphones

Works with Apple iPhone 7 Smart Battery Case

Made for iPhone + iPad

Description:

Sleep better, live better

Name: Fitbit Sense Fitness Wristband Heart Rate Tracker White/Gold
Short description:
• Up to 6 Days of Battery Life
  • Heart Rate Monitoring
  • Built-In AMOLED Display
  • Swimproof Construction
  • SmartTrack Automatic Activity Detection
  • Built-In GPS Tracking
  • On-Wrist Skin Temperature Sensor
  • Stress Detection & Tracking
  • Female Health Tracking
  • Call, Text & App Notifications
Description:
Track your health and fitness with the Sense GPS Smartwatch from Fitbit. It's essential to maintain good health to better achieve your fitness goals, which is why Fitbit incorporates a variety of health tracking options in the Sense smartwatch. Features like an on-wrist EDA scan app to detect electrodermal activity. This tracks your stress and graphs it, letting you track trends and change habits to reduce stress. You also get on-wrist heart rate monitoring with an ECG app to help assess a possible AFib condition, SpO2, a skin temperature sensor, and sleep tracking.

When it comes to fitness, a built-in GPS lets you track outdoor activities without the need of a smartphone. You can select from over 20 goal-based exercise modes or let the Sense's SmartTrack technology automatically detect and track your workout. Even basic daily activities are tracked, such as steps taken, distance traveled, and more. Bring your smartphone along to stay motivated with access to Spotify, Deezer, Pandora, and more. Outside of health and fitness, this smartwatch keeps you connected with call, text, and app notifications, voice control of digital assistants, and access to hundreds of apps that allow the Fitbit Sense to fully integrate into your day to day life.

Fitbit Premium
For new Premium users, you will receive a free 6 months of Fitbit Premium. Premium provides you with guided workouts, help with nutrition, personalized insights into your fitness, stress management tools, and much more.
Health Features
ECG app notifies you when your heart rate rises or falls past your personal thresholds
Skin temperature sensor records nightly variations you can track over time
PurePulse 2.0 24/7 heart rate monitoring
See real-time heart rate stats on screen when you are in a cardio, peak, or fat burn zones
Women can log periods, record symptoms, track ovulation and discover menstrual cycle patterns
See how much light, deep, and REM sleep you get each night
Receive a sleep score each night in the Fitbit app to monitor sleep quality over time
Mute notifications to gain better uninterrupted sleep
With Smart Wake, you can set an alarm to peacefully wake to a quiet vibration
Fitness Features
Up to 164' of water resistance lets you use the Fitbit Sense in the pool or at the beach
Workout intensity map in the Fitbit app lets you track heart rate zones throughout your exercises
Earn Active Zone Minutes and receive a buzz on your wrist as you enter personalized target zones
All day activity tracking records steps taken, distance traveled, floors climbed, total active minutes, and calories burned
Smart Features
Get information and operate functions on your mobile device via Google Assistant or Alexa
Receive call, text, and calendar notifications
Send quick text or voice replies to texts directly from the Fitbit Sense (Android Only)
Use Fitbit Pay to tap and pay for purchases using your smartwatch
Choose from hundreds of apps that cover many aspects of your daily life, such as Uber, United Airlines, TRX, and more
The always-on display function lets you monitor your stats with just a glance
Customize the display with hundreds of clock face options online
Store up to 5 clock faces on the Sense
General Features
Over 6 days of battery life
AMOLED display with laser-bonded Corning Gorilla Glass 3
Do Not Disturb mode mutes calls, texts, calendar, and app notifications
Get up to 24 hours of power in just 12 minutes with fast charging
Soft, lightweight, and flexible Infinity band
Compatible with the Fitbit app for viewing stats, taking part in group challenges, and much more
Categories: Smart Watches, Smart Watches > Smart Watches

Short description:
• 16000 CPI

Description:
Bloody A4 Bloody X5 Pro is a real pro-gaming: the professional Pro 3389 sensor with 16000 CPI, 12000 FPS, 400 IPS and 50g acceleration guarantees high performance and accuracy.

CPI customization (50-16000 CPI for A4 Bloody X5 Pro) and five CPI presets (400-800-1000-1600-3200 CPI) provide exceptional tracking accuracy and consistent response to any speed. At the same time, both models differ in lightning-fast response: the response speed is only one millisecond.

Four levels of polling rate make it possible to switch between the available values ​​(125, 500, 1000, 2000 Hz) and choose exactly the one that best suits a particular gaming session. For the best possible accuracy and controllability, you can adjust the LOD to suit your gaming habits and choose the appropriate lift-off height: 1.5mm, 2mm and 3mm LODs.

The durable scroll wheel provides tactile comfort while playing and also provides

durability of the device. For an ergonomic and comfortable fit of the hand, a premium anti-slip coating on the side surfaces is provided. RGB lighting can be customized as desired by choosing any of 12 effects.

Description:
JBL JBLCLIP4BLKAM Clip 4 Black Portable Bluetooth Speaker

Clip and Play. Cool, portable, and waterproof. The vibrant fresh looking JBL Clip 4 delivers surprisingly rich JBL Original Pro Sound in a compact package. The unique oval shape fits easy in your hand. Fully wrapped in colorful fabrics with expressive details inspired by current street fashion, it’s easy to match your style. The fully integrated carabiner hooks instantly to bags, belts, or buckles, to bring your favorite tunes anywhere. Waterproof, dustproof, and up to 10 hours of playtime, it’s rugged enough to tag along wherever you explore. Features
  • Rich JBL Original Pro Sound JBL Pro Sound delivers surprisingly rich audio and punchy bass from Clip 4’s compact size.
  • Bold style and ultra-portable design JBL Clip 4’s ultra-portable design goes great with the latest styles, and its colorful fabrics and expressive details make it look as great as it sounds.

  • IP67 waterproof and dustproof To the pool. To the park. JBL Clip 4 is IP67 waterproof and dustproof, so you can bring your speaker anywhere.
  • Wireless Bluetooth streaming Wirelessly stream music from your phone, tablet, or any other Bluetooth-enabled device.
  • 10 hours of battery life Don’t sweat the small stuff like charging your battery. JBL Clip 4 gives you up to 10 hours of playtime on a single charge.
  • Vibrant color options JBL Clip 4 features exclusive colorways inspired by the latest street fashion trends, introducing completely new shades and combinations.

  • Transducer: 40mm / 1.5"

  • Music play time: up to 10 hours (varies by volume level and audio content)

  • Bluetooth® profile: A2DP 1.3, AVRCP 1.6

  • Bluetooth® transmitter power: ≤10 dBm (EIRP)
  • Bluetooth® transmitter modulation: GFSK, π/4 DQPSK, 8DPSK

Name: JBL QUANTUM200 Wired Over Ear Gaming Headset Black
Description:
In competitive gaming, sound is survival, and JBL knows great sound: From the thrill of tracking enemies in FPS games, to engaging in epic MOBA battles, the JBL Quantum 200 amplifies every victory on PC, Mac, Xbox, PS4 and Nintendo Switch.

Features JBL Quantum Sound Signature which is engineered for accuracy and delivers immersive gaming audio for a competitive edge, so users never have to miss a step, shot or jump during gameplay

JBL Quantum 200 gaming headset incorporates a flip-up boom microphone with echo cancelling technology, allowing users to focus on their teammates' voice rather than background noise, for crystal clear communication.

Memory foam ear cushions on the JBL Quantum 200 gaming headset are covered in soft PU leather, providing comfort for marathon sessions, plus 3.5 millimeter and PC splitter connections for multi-platform gaming on PC, Mac, Xbox, PS4 and Nintendo Switch.

Items delivered: JBL Quantum 200 wired over ear gaming headset with flip-up boom mic in black, compatible with PC, Mac, Xbox, PlayStation, Nintendo Switch, mobile and VR.

Name: Beats Flex All-Day Wireless Earphones Yellow
Short description:
• Magnetic earbuds with Auto-Play/Pause
  • Custom acoustic platform delivers premium sound with accurate bass and low distortion
  • Built-in microphone with wind reduction for elevated voice clarity
  • Up to 12 hours of listening time
  • All-day comfort with Flex-Form cable and four ear tip options
  • Powered by the Apple W1 chip for seamless connectivity
  • Audio Sharing lets you wirelessly share audio with another pair of Beats headphones or AirPods
  • 10-minute Fast Fuel charging gives 1.5 hours of playback
  • Class 1 Bluetooth® for extended range and fewer dropouts
  • On-device controls for volume, track and call controls located on the left side of neckband housing
  • Power button located on the right side of neckband housing
Description: Flex All Day In your ears or around your neck, Beats Flex are as versatile as the life you lead. Whether you’re listening to music, taking calls, or scrolling your social feed, you’ll always be ready for what’s next. Magnetic earbuds make listening that much easier by automatically playing music when they’re in your ears and pausing when they’re attached around your neck. The Flex-Form cable provides all-day comfort with durable Nitinol construction while four eartip options offer a personalized fit. And when you’re not wearing them, the magnetic earbuds keep Beats Flex tangle-free as they easily coil up into your pocket or purse. Driven by Premium Sound Beats Flex employs a dual-chamber acoustic design and a proprietary layered driver to achieve outstanding stereo separation with rich and precise bass response. Laser cut micro-venting provides ear pressure relief, and the optimized driver angle ensures clear, crisp sound. An advanced digital processor fine-tunes your audio for an accurate and emotive listening experience. The result — rich, powerful sound that keeps you inspired all day long.
